NK005(ca)013:1576: phyi sgo srung ba'i ya ma r+aa dza la thim pas gnyis su med par gyur /
NK005(ca)013:1578: lag pa dpung mgor bsnol ba'i sdigs mdzub sbreng ste /
NK005(ca)013:1579: b+h+r+aum kha ta pra be sha ya phata /
NK005(ca)013:1580: ces pas khog pa'i sgo dbye /
NK005(ca)013:1582: zhes pas 'bar ba'i lta bas mched lcam thams cad nang du zhugs /
NK005(ca)013:1584: zhes phyir nud de sgo rbad kyis bcad par bsgom /
NK005(ca)013:1585: de nas rdo rje'i 'gros kyis man+dala bskor zhing /
NK005(ca)013:1588: stong gsum thams cad h'u du me re re gyur //
NK005(ca)013:1590: rdo rje me dpung gi gur du gyur par bsgom zhing /
NK005(ca)013:1592: steng yang rdo rje'i bla bre la //
NK005(ca)013:1593: sogs gong bzhin brjod la mtshams bcad /
NK005(ca)013:1595: bdag gi smin mtshams nas b+h+r+aum 'od zer dang bcas
NK005(ca)013:1596: pa brgyad ma tram gyi gnas brgyad la 'phros pas
NK005(ca)013:1598: dpal rang byung gi mchod rten brgyad kyi gzhal yas
NK005(ca)013:1599: khang du gyur pa la dur khrod kyi ma mo
NK005(ca)013:1600: brgyad byon te bzhugs par mos la /
NK005(ca)013:1601: rol mo bshugs glu gsur dud zhing g.yab dbyangs dang bcas te /
NK005(ca)013:1603: sngon tshe 'das dus dang po la //
NK005(ca)013:1604: bcom ldan dpal chen he ru kas //
NK005(ca)013:1605: dur khrod bdag po ma tram bsgral //
NK005(ca)013:1606: bor nas sa gzhir gyur pa la //
NK005(ca)013:1607: ro yi srung ma chen po ni //
NK005(ca)013:1608: ma mo chen mo brgyad bzhag go //
NK005(ca)013:1609: de yi gnas rten chen po yang //
NK005(ca)013:1610: mchod rten chen po gzi byin can //
NK005(ca)013:1611: rang byung re re bzhag pa yin //
NK005(ca)013:1612: de ltar sa gzhi 'di kun yang //
NK005(ca)013:1613: bkra shis ya mtshan thugs rje can //
NK005(ca)013:1614: chos dang dngos grub 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK005(ca)013:1616: dur khrod chen po gnas brgyad nas //
NK005(ca)013:1617: ma mo chen mo spyan 'dren no //
NK005(ca)013:1618: de yi lus snying ma ga ta //
NK005(ca)013:1619: dur khrod chen po bsil ba'i tshal //
NK005(ca)013:1620: mchod rten bde byed rten srung ba'i //
NK005(ca)013:1621: ma mo chen mo ke'u r+ai ma //
NK005(ca)013:1622: mkhas shing snying stobs che sa nas //
NK005(ca)013:1623: gang dmigs len pa'i mkha' 'gro ma //
NK005(ca)013:1624: ke'u r+ai chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:1625: de yi mgo bo lho yi phyogs //
NK005(ca)013:1626: dur khrod chen po sing+ga gling //
NK005(ca)013:1627: mchod rten ri bo ta la srung //
NK005(ca)013:1628: ma mo chen mo tsoo'u r+ai ma //
NK005(ca)013:1629: mthong chos rnam par 'khrul sa nas //
NK005(ca)013:1631: tsoo'u r+ai chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:1632: lag pa g.yas pa shar lho mtshams //
NK005(ca)013:1633: dur khrod chen po bal yul na //
NK005(ca)013:1634: mchod rten ag sho b+y+aa kri srung //
NK005(ca)013:1635: ma mo chen mo puk+ka s+ai //
NK005(ca)013:1636: zas kyi longs spyod che sa nas //
NK005(ca)013:1638: puk+ka chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:1639: lag pa g.yon pa lho nub mtshams //
NK005(ca)013:1640: dur khrod chen mo s+aa l+ai yul //
NK005(ca)013:1641: gyad yul mchod rten sgo mang srung //
NK005(ca)013:1642: ma mo chen mo be t+wa l+ai //
NK005(ca)013:1643: mthu dang dbang yang che sa nas //
NK005(ca)013:1644: gsod par byed pa'i mkha' 'gro ma //
NK005(ca)013:1645: be t+aa chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:1646: rkang pa g.yas pa byang shar mtshams //
NK005(ca)013:1647: dur khrod chen mo li yi yul //
NK005(ca)013:1648: mchod rten go'u de shan srung //
NK005(ca)013:1649: ma mo chen mo tsan d+ha l+ai //
NK005(ca)013:1650: me chu rdzu 'phrul che sa nas //
NK005(ca)013:1652: tsan d+ha chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:1653: rkang pa g.yon pa nub byang mtshams //
NK005(ca)013:1654: dur khrod chen po kha che'i yul //
NK005(ca)013:1655: mchod rten ka ni ka srung ba'i //
NK005(ca)013:1656: ma mo tshan mo pra mo h+aa //
NK005(ca)013:1657: bde skyid ldan pa'i yul dag nas //
NK005(ca)013:1658: len cing zlog pa'i mkha' 'gro ma //
NK005(ca)013:1659: pra mo chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:1660: pho mtshan steng gi byang phyogs nas //
NK005(ca)013:1661: dur khrod chen po u rgyan yul //
NK005(ca)013:1662: mchod rten dar ma tsakra srung //
NK005(ca)013:1663: ma mo chen mo gasma ri //
NK005(ca)013:1664: dngos grub can yang de na mang //
NK005(ca)013:1665: smyo bar byed pa'i mkha' 'gro ma //
NK005(ca)013:1666: gasma chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:1667: de yi nang rol thams cad kun //
NK005(ca)013:1668: dur khrod chen mo za hor yul //
NK005(ca)013:1669: mchod rten bde byed gzhon nu srung //
NK005(ca)013:1670: ma mo chen mo sma sha ni //
NK005(ca)013:1671: 'byor pa'i longs spyod che sa nas //
NK005(ca)013:1672: gsod par byed pa'i mkha' 'gro ma //
NK005(ca)013:1673: sma sha chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:1674: ma mo brgyad po gshegs nas kyang //
NK005(ca)013:1675: dngos grub stsol zhing brtan par bzhugs //
NK005(ca)013:1677: bdag gi phyag na gnas pa'i ye shes kyi ko'u
NK005(ca)013:1678: r+ai ma brgyad las gnyis pa 'phros te dbang bskur
NK005(ca)013:1679: bas las dang ye shes dbyer med pas srung ba'i
NK005(ca)013:1681: gzhan yang dug gsum sha khrag rus pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK005(ca)013:1682: du mche gshog la sogs pa'i phra men ma sprul
NK005(ca)013:1683: pa du ma dang bcas pas dgra bgegs tshar gcod
NK005(ca)013:1684: pa'i phrin las mdzad par gyur /
NK005(ca)013:1685: ces bsgoms la bskor ba lan gsum bya'o //
NK005(ca)013:1687: ma tram gi gnas bzhir las bzhi so so'i sbyin
NK005(ca)013:1688: sreg bya bar bshad kyang lag tu mi lon pas
NK005(ca)013:1689: las bzhi'i rta bro brdung ba ni /
NK005(ca)013:1690: bro ra las bzhi'i dbyibs mtshungs so sor bskor la /
NK005(ca)013:1691: snang srid dbang gi dkyil 'khor du bdag nyid pad+ma
NK005(ca)013:1692: he ru ka yab yum 'khor dang bcas pas rdo
NK005(ca)013:1693: rje'i bro brdung bar bsam la /
NK005(ca)013:1694: wam gi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)013:1695: lu gu rgyud du sbrel nas bsdoms //
NK005(ca)013:1698: gdong nas ma byung bdud la sogs //
NK005(ca)013:1699: rgyal po de dang de dag gis //
NK005(ca)013:1700: lan cig dur khrod bcas pa'i tshe //
NK005(ca)013:1701: gdug pa rnams kyi khrag za zhing //
NK005(ca)013:1702: khro bo chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK005(ca)013:1704: thang cig yud la drongs la shog /
NK005(ca)013:1705: h+r+aihche ge mo bam h+r+aih skyes kyang 'dod chags khyod las skyes //
NK005(ca)013:1707: 'dod chags las kyi ru dra khyod //
NK005(ca)013:1709: zangs sam dmar bo'i shing rnams la //
NK005(ca)013:1710: mgo la rgya mdud rtse zla gam //
NK005(ca)013:1711: logs la dbang gi lha bsgoms nas //
NK005(ca)013:1712: khong stong byang chub sems lung bstan //
NK005(ca)013:1713: btab na thams cad dbang du 'gyur //
NK005(ca)013:1714: bam h+r+aim ma ma p+aa sham ku ru h+r+aih snang
NK005(ca)013:1715: srid drag po'i dkyil 'khor du bdag nyid badz+ra he
NK005(ca)013:1716: ru ka yab yum 'khor dang bcas bar bsam la
NK005(ca)013:1717: / e yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)013:1718: lu gu rgyud du sbrel nas bsdoms //
NK005(ca)013:1719: bcings 'gyur bskyod nas phyogs bcur g.yo //
NK005(ca)013:1720: myos nas gal te tshig par 'gyur //
NK005(ca)013:1721: gdod nas ma byung bdud la sogs //
NK005(ca)013:1722: rgyal po de dang de dag gis //
NK005(ca)013:1723: lan cig dur khrod bcas pa'i tshe //
NK005(ca)013:1724: gdug pa rnams kyi khrag za zhing //
NK005(ca)013:1725: khro bo chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK005(ca)013:1727: thang cig yud la drongs la shog /
NK005(ca)013:1728: h'u phata che ge mo h'u dzah skyes kyang zhe sdang khyod las skyes //
NK005(ca)013:1730: zhe sdang las kyi ru dra khyod //
NK005(ca)013:1731: zhe sdang khro bo 'khor bcas kyis //
NK005(ca)013:1732: lcags sam nag po'i shing rnams la //
NK005(ca)013:1733: mgo la rgya mdud rtse zur gsum //
NK005(ca)013:1734: logs la drag po'i lha bsgoms nas //
NK005(ca)013:1735: khong stong byang chub sems lung bstan //
NK005(ca)013:1736: btab na thams cad brlag par 'gyur //
NK005(ca)013:1737: h'u phata m+aa ra ya phata /
NK005(ca)013:1738: snang srid zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor du bdag nyid bud+d+ha
NK005(ca)013:1739: he ru ka yab yum 'khor dang bcas pas rdo
NK005(ca)013:1740: rje'i bro brdung bar bsam la /
NK005(ca)013:1741: ya yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)013:1742: lu gu rgyud du sbrel nas bsdoms //
NK005(ca)013:1743: 'bar ba lhan ner byin gyis khyab //
NK005(ca)013:1744: thams cad g.yo ba med par byed //
NK005(ca)013:1745: gdod nas ma byung bdud la sogs //
NK005(ca)013:1746: rgyal po de dang de dag gis //
NK005(ca)013:1747: lan cig dur khrod bcas pa'i tshe //
NK005(ca)013:1748: gdug pa rnams kyi khrag za zhing //
NK005(ca)013:1749: khro bo chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK005(ca)013:1751: thang cig yud la drongs la shog /
NK005(ca)013:1752: s+w+aa che ge mo s+w+aa dzah skyes kyang gti mug khyod las skyes //
NK005(ca)013:1754: gti mug las kyi ru dra khyod //
NK005(ca)013:1755: gti mug khro bo 'khor bcas kyis //
NK005(ca)013:1756: dngul lam dkar po'i shing rnams la //
NK005(ca)013:1757: mgo la rgya mdud rtse zlum po //
NK005(ca)013:1758: logs la zhi ba'i lha bsgoms nas //
NK005(ca)013:1759: khong stong byang chub sems lung bstan //
NK005(ca)013:1760: btab na thams cad zhi bar 'gyur //
NK005(ca)013:1761: s+w+aa sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)013:1762: snang srid rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor du bdag nyid rat+na
NK005(ca)013:1763: he ru ka yab yum 'khor dang bcas pas rdo
NK005(ca)013:1764: rje'i bro brdung bar bsam la /
NK005(ca)013:1765: ma yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)013:1766: lu gu rgyud du sbrel bsdoms bskyod //
NK005(ca)013:1768: yid bzhin nam mkha' gang bar 'gyur //
NK005(ca)013:1769: gdod nas ma byung bdud la sogs //
NK005(ca)013:1770: rgyal po de dang de dag gis //
NK005(ca)013:1771: lan cig dur khrod bcas pa'i tshe //
NK005(ca)013:1772: gdug pa rnams kyi khrag za zhing //
NK005(ca)013:1773: khro bo chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK005(ca)013:1775: thang cig yud la drongs la shog /
NK005(ca)013:1776: h+aa che ge mo h+aa dzah skyes kyang nga rgyal khyod las skyes //
NK005(ca)013:1778: nga rgyal las kyi ru dra khyod //
NK005(ca)013:1779: nga rgyal khro bo 'khor bcas kyis //
NK005(ca)013:1780: gser ram ser po'i shing rnams la //
NK005(ca)013:1781: mgo la rgya bdud rtse zur bzhi //
NK005(ca)013:1782: logs la rgyas pa'i lha bsgoms nas //
NK005(ca)013:1783: khong stong byang chub sems lung bstan //
NK005(ca)013:1784: btab na thams cad rgyas par 'gyur //
NK005(ca)013:1785: s+w+aa push+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)013:1787: bdag nyid dpal chen po'i thugs ka'i 'od zer gyis
NK005(ca)013:1788: 'khor 'das kyi tshe bcud bsdus te bdag nyid rdo
NK005(ca)013:1789: rje'i tshe grub par mos la /
NK005(ca)013:1790: b+h+r+aum badz+ra +aa yu she h'u ah ci rigs bzlas la shis brjod bya'o //
NK005(ca)013:1791: phrin las 'di ni dgos pa shin tu che bas
NK005(ca)013:1792: skabs 'dir ma zad sgrub pa'i skabs skabs su bya
NK005(ca)013:1794: rtsa ba'i gsum gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor bri zhing rdzas dgod pa'i phrin las la bzhi /
NK005(ca)013:1801: stegs bu 'dom gang gru bzhi pa //
NK005(ca)013:1802: 'phang du gru gang ba yi tshad //
NK005(ca)013:1803: ba byung sna lngas skyang nul bya //
NK005(ca)013:1806: dung phor du byang sems dkar dmar dngos sam /
NK005(ca)013:1807: ma 'byor na cu gang dang sin+d+hu ra'i chab kyis chag chag gdab la /
NK005(ca)013:1809: bka' gsang rmad du byung ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK005(ca)013:1810: 'khor ba'i rgyun gcod byang chub sems kyi ngang //
NK005(ca)013:1811: mkha' dbyings rnam dag yum gyi gzhal yas su //
NK005(ca)013:1812: rak+ta gsang ba'i thig le chen por spro //
NK005(ca)013:1813: ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+dala h'u /
NK005(ca)013:1815: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)013:1816: gdod nas dag pa'i dri med byang chub sems //
NK005(ca)013:1817: ye shes rang byung chen po bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK005(ca)013:1818: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor chen po chag chag 'debs //
NK005(ca)013:1819: ma h+aa bo d+hi tsit+ta man+da la h'u /
NK005(ca)013:1820: thod snod du bdud rtsi sbyar ba'i byugs pa btang la /
NK005(ca)013:1822: dug lnga rnam dag sku lngar lhun gyis grub //
NK005(ca)013:1823: gdod nas dag pa'i bdud rtsi go ma yi //
NK005(ca)013:1824: shes rab yum gyi mkha' la rgyud ltar gsal //
NK005(ca)013:1825: dur khrod gsang ba'i bzhugs gnas thig ler shar //
NK005(ca)013:1826: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta man+dala h'u /
NK005(ca)013:1827: zhes brjod la snyoms par byug /
NK005(ca)013:1829: rgyas par spro na rgyud dang gsang 'grel sgra ji bzhin pa bya dgos la /
NK005(ca)013:1830: lag len dkyus ma tsam ni dkyil chog bdud rtsi'i nying khu las 'byung ba ltar lag tu blang /
NK005(ca)013:1831: gal te rdul tshon gyi bya ba mi lcogs na
NK005(ca)013:1832: skabs 'dir ras bris kyi dkyil 'khor dgram par bya'o
NK005(ca)013:1839: snga ma dang zhag gis bar du bcad na 'dir
NK005(ca)013:1840: yang ba dag bskyed bzlas pa dang bcas pa rgyas
NK005(ca)013:1841: bsdus gang yang rung bar bya /
NK005(ca)013:1844: dbus su rgyal rigs dum bu gcig /
NK005(ca)013:1845: phyogs bzhir bram ze rgyas rigs dang //
NK005(ca)013:1846: rje'u rigs dmangs rigs bzhi la bya //
NK005(ca)013:1847: mtshams bzhir khrus mkhan gar mkhan dang //
NK005(ca)013:1848: rje'u rigs gtso glag mkhan rnams la //
NK005(ca)013:1849: mi yi khrag la snag tsha bya //
NK005(ca)013:1850: mchog gi rkang gi smyu gu yis //
NK005(ca)013:1851: lha dgu so so'i snying po bri //
NK005(ca)013:1852: ban+d+ha'i mtshan gsol bzhugs su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:1853: ces gsungs pa ltar so so 'tshogs na mchog tu gyur kyang /
NK005(ca)013:1854: mi 'dzom na der brtags pa'i thod pa mtshan ldan
NK005(ca)013:1855: dum bu gcig pa'i nang du rdo rje dang kha
NK005(ca)013:1856: t+w+aam gtso bo'i sngags rnams byang sems dkar dmar gyis
NK005(ca)013:1857: bris pa dang / thod tshal la ma mo brgyad kyi phyag mtshan dang sngags bris pa /
NK005(ca)013:1858: yang na bka' brgyad spyi'i phyag srol ltar sku yongs rdzogs bris na'ang /
NK005(ca)013:1859: rdo rje dang dril bu dar sngon pos so sor bcings pa /
NK005(ca)013:1860: thod tshal zla gam pad+ma bris pa'i dbus su rdo
NK005(ca)013:1861: rje'i shar bu pad+ma'i ze'u 'bru sbyar ba la dur
NK005(ca)013:1862: khrod kyi ras kyis dkris pa'i sdong bu btsugs pa
NK005(ca)013:1863: la sha lnga'i rgyu las byung ba'i tshil rkang zhag
NK005(ca)013:1864: dang 'bru mar rtsi mar rnams kyis bkang ba'i mar
NK005(ca)013:1865: me dgu / de dag kyang ji bzhin ma tshogs
NK005(ca)013:1866: na snod khams sogs la dbyibs der bcos shing snod
NK005(ca)013:1867: der mos pas brtags shing bcud ji ltar tshogs pa
NK005(ca)013:1868: me dgu / bya / de ltar na ban+d+ha sku /
NK005(ca)013:1870: mar me thugs te rgyud nas gsungs pa'i sgrub rdzas gtso bo yin la /
NK005(ca)013:1871: gzhan yang dbang bskur na bum pa sogs dbang rdzas rnams dang /
NK005(ca)013:1872: 'dzin gtor ram sgrub gtor pad snod du dpal bshos
NK005(ca)013:1873: dmar po rak+ta'i thig le can gtso 'khor dgu mtheb
NK005(ca)013:1874: kyu dang bcas pa la tsakli sngags byang me long
NK005(ca)013:1875: dar gdugs mthing nag gis spras pa /
NK005(ca)013:1876: rgyan rdzas zhing chen gyi bla bre /
NK005(ca)013:1877: zur bzhir mi mgo dang tsit+ta'i tog can gyi rgyal mtshan /
NK005(ca)013:1878: rgyu ma'i lda ldi dang d+r+wa phyed /
NK005(ca)013:1882: ro ras kyi yol ba rnams so //
NK005(ca)013:1883: spyi mthun sgab skor mda' ral gri tshon skud kyi
NK005(ca)013:1884: d+r+wa ba la sogs pa ji ltar 'byor ba rnams
NK005(ca)013:1885: dang / mchod rdzas chu gnyis nyer spyod zhi drag /
NK005(ca)013:1886: dpal gyi gtor ma rak+ta'i thig le dgu btab pa /
NK005(ca)013:1887: rtsa brgyad stong sbyar bdud rtsi /
NK005(ca)013:1888: rak+ta so lnga sbyar ba'i khrag zhal /
NK005(ca)013:1889: zhal zas sna tshogs pa'i gtor ma la sogs pa
NK005(ca)013:1890: 'og tu dgos pa'i yo byad thams cad tshang ba
NK005(ca)013:1891: dkyil 'khor gyi mdun stegs su bzhag la /
NK005(ca)013:1892: zhe sdang rdo rje'i ting 'dzin gyis /
NK005(ca)013:1896: gu gul yungs thun sogs tsham rngams kyis bgegs bskrad /
NK005(ca)013:1897: ru lu'i dzapa dbyangs lan gsum blang ba dang lhan cig rdor slob kyis dril spos kyis sna drangs /
NK005(ca)013:1898: rgyal thebs gzungs ma las rdor sogs kyi rdzas rnams
NK005(ca)013:1899: go rim bzhin thogs te dkyil 'khor la lan gsum
NK005(ca)013:1900: bskor ba'i mthar mdun phyogs su 'khod la /
NK005(ca)013:1902: dbus nas rang byung grub pa'i lha //
NK005(ca)013:1903: thugs mchog badz+ra he ru ka /
NK005(ca)013:1904: badz+ra kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai gnyis //
NK005(ca)013:1905: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor chen po nas //
NK005(ca)013:1906: dzahmh'u bam hohs spyan drangs shing //
NK005(ca)013:1907: dur khrod chen po'i gnas mchog dang //
NK005(ca)013:1909: lha chen bsnol ba'i gdan steng du //
NK005(ca)013:1910: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:1911: thabs kyi rgyal po dpal chen nyid kyi gnas //
NK005(ca)013:1912: pho brang rtags dang ldan pas snod bcud rgyan du che //
NK005(ca)013:1913: sprul pa lcang lo mang po'i kha bad can //
NK005(ca)013:1914: dbang po rna lnga snod bcud rgyan bkram nas //
NK005(ca)013:1915: mi gnas dpal chen yab yum bzhugs pa'i rten du 'bul //
NK005(ca)013:1917: badz+ra kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)013:1919: zhes brjod la thod pa gtso bo dbus su bzhag /
NK005(ca)013:1920: de'ang gsang 'grel las dbus kyi zla gam la ban+d+ha'i
NK005(ca)013:1921: kha nub bstan gyis sbubs la dpal chen po yab
NK005(ca)013:1922: yum thabs shes zung 'brel 'khril nas bzhugs par bsgom
NK005(ca)013:1923: par gsungs kyang / deng sang lag len du 'di
NK005(ca)013:1924: rigs 'bru'i snod du dbu gyen bstan du 'jog par
NK005(ca)013:1925: mdzad snang ba tha mal pa'i mig lam du mdzes
NK005(ca)013:1926: cha btsal bar mngon pas rtog pa la gang shong
NK005(ca)013:1927: par gsungs kyang / bya'o // de'i rjes 'brel du /
NK005(ca)013:1929: rdo rje'i rigs mchog chen po ste //
NK005(ca)013:1930: rdo rje dril bu rig pa 'dzin //
NK005(ca)013:1931: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su ldan //
NK005(ca)013:1932: rtags kyi phyag rgyar bzhugs su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:1935: zhes rdo rje g.yas su bkod /
NK005(ca)013:1936: d+harma d+h+aa tu g+han+de hoh sa ma ya tish+tha lhan /
NK005(ca)013:1937: zhes dril bu g.yon nas brten te bkod /
NK005(ca)013:1938: de nas ma mo brgyad kyi rten thod rim bzhin thogs la /
NK005(ca)013:1940: dur khrod gnas brgyad 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NK005(ca)013:1941: ma chen 'bar ma brgyad rnams gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:1942: h'u ma mo chen mo me 'bar ma //
NK005(ca)013:1943: ke'u ri chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:1944: mthing nag 'bar ba'i ral pa can //
NK005(ca)013:1945: sngon tshe ye shes bsnyen cing bsgrubs //
NK005(ca)013:1946: sngon gyi thugs dam bdag dang gcig /
NK005(ca)013:1948: mchog phran bsnol ba'i gdan steng du //
NK005(ca)013:1949: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:1950: badz+ra ke'u r+ai ha sa ma ya tish+tha badz+ra /
NK005(ca)013:1952: ma mo chen mo me 'bar ma //
NK005(ca)013:1953: tsoo'u r+ai chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:1954: ser nag 'bar ba'i ral pa can //
NK005(ca)013:1955: sngon tshe ye shes bsnyen cing bsgrubs //
NK005(ca)013:1956: sngon gyi dur khrod mchog phran dgyes shing badz+ra tsoo'u r+ai ha sa ma ya tish+tha badz+ra /
NK005(ca)013:1958: ma mo chen mo me phra men chen mo dmar
NK005(ca)013:1959: nag 'bar sngon tshe sngon gyi dur khrod mchog phran
NK005(ca)013:1960: dgyes shing badz+ra pra mo h+aa he sa ma ya
NK005(ca)013:1962: ma mo chen mo me be ta chen mo mthing
NK005(ca)013:1963: nag 'bar ba'i sngon tshe sngon gyi dur khrod mchog
NK005(ca)013:1964: phran dgyes shing badz+ra be ta l+ai ha sa ma
NK005(ca)013:1965: ya tish+tha h'u / ma mo chen mo me 'bar
NK005(ca)013:1966: puk+ka chen mo dmar ser 'bar ba'i sngon tshe sngon
NK005(ca)013:1967: gyi dur khrod mchog phran dgyes shing badz+ra puk+ka s+ai
NK005(ca)013:1968: ha sa ma ya tish+tha h'u /
NK005(ca)013:1969: ma mo chen mo kasma chen ljang ser 'bar ba'i
NK005(ca)013:1970: sngon tshe sngon gyi dur khrod mchog phran dgyes shing
NK005(ca)013:1971: badz+ra g+hasma r+ai ha sa ma ya tish+tha h'u /
NK005(ca)013:1972: ma mo chen mo sma sha chen mo mthing nag
NK005(ca)013:1973: 'bar sngon tshe sngon gyi dur khrod mchog phran dgyes
NK005(ca)013:1974: shing badz+ra sma sha n+ai ha sa ma ya tish+tha
NK005(ca)013:1975: h'u / ma mo chen mo tsan+d+ha chen mo ser
NK005(ca)013:1976: skya 'bar ba'i sngon tshe sngon gyi dur khrod mchog
NK005(ca)013:1977: phran dgyes shing badz+ra tsan+d+ha l+ai ha sa ma ya
NK005(ca)013:1978: tish+tha zhes shar sogs phyogs bzhi dang shar lho sogs
NK005(ca)013:1979: mtshams bzhir g.yas bskor gyis gtso bo la zhal bstan
NK005(ca)013:1980: h'u / te bkod do // gnyis pa ni /
NK005(ca)013:1981: mar me dgu po thogs la /
NK005(ca)013:1983: skye med chos kyi dbyings nyid las //
NK005(ca)013:1984: dur khrod chen po'i gzhal yas khang //
NK005(ca)013:1985: zla gam dbang gi dkyil 'khor gsal //
NK005(ca)013:1986: dbang phyug mchog bran gdan steng na //
NK005(ca)013:1987: yang dag don gyi lha dgu ru //
NK005(ca)013:1988: rang bzhin 'od gsal ye shes dgu //
NK005(ca)013:1989: sgrib pa dgu po rang gsal phyir //
NK005(ca)013:1990: dmigs med gsal rtog med tshul gyis //
NK005(ca)013:1991: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:1992: dz+ny+aa na d+ai pa +aa lo ke dz+wa la tish+tha lhan /
NK005(ca)013:1993: ces brjod la rten thod dgu dang 'brel chags su dgod do //
NK005(ca)013:1995: dbang gi skabs sngar sta gon byas pa'i bum pa rnams steng gi lding khri la bzhag /
NK005(ca)013:1996: las bum byang shar gyi grwar bkod /
NK005(ca)013:1997: tsaka li'ang bum pa dang lhan cig bzhag /
NK005(ca)013:2000: ban+d+ha mtshan ldan chang dang sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga
NK005(ca)013:2001: snying po lngas bkang ba'i nang du bzang shing gi
NK005(ca)013:2002: byang bu'am gro ga lta bur /
NK005(ca)013:2003: bdag sgrub pa po rdo rje che ge mo la
NK005(ca)013:2004: mchog thun mong gnyis kyi dngos grub myur du stsol
NK005(ca)013:2005: cig / lta bu dngos grub kyi gsol byang sgrub pa po du yod kyi grangs mnyam mam /
NK005(ca)013:2006: bdag rdo rje rgyal po 'di zhes bya bas gtsor byas /
NK005(ca)013:2007: rdo rje mched lcam grangs 'di tsam zhes phyogs gcig
NK005(ca)013:2008: bsdoms pa'i byang bu gcig byas kyang stabs bde bas
NK005(ca)013:2009: / gang ltar spra rtsi'am mar gyis byugs pa bcug /
NK005(ca)013:2010: mi bde na thod pa'i khar bzhag kyang rung la de dang rdo rje tshe ste zan /
NK005(ca)013:2011: de'ang mngar gsum sbyar ba'i ril bu bya /
NK005(ca)013:2013: dza gad dam dpa' byed de chang /
NK005(ca)013:2014: 'jam des sam zla ba dkar ba ste mar /
NK005(ca)013:2015: zla rgyas te zho dang khur ba /
NK005(ca)013:2016: zla phram ste thud dang khrum /
NK005(ca)013:2017: gal phyis te spod sna tshogs kyi g.yos /
NK005(ca)013:2022: sham mo ste sing po sogs bza' bca' btung ba'i
NK005(ca)013:2023: bye brag mang po dang lhan cig shar sgor bzhag
NK005(ca)013:2025: sman raka gtor gsum sogs dkyus kyi phyag len ltar bkod /
NK005(ca)013:2026: brgya rtsa'am stong mchod sogs spros 'byor che na'ang tshul dang mthun par bsham /
NK005(ca)013:2027: steng 'og bar gsum mtha' skor gyi rgyan rnams kyang mthong brgyud ltar bkram la /
NK005(ca)013:2029: zhing bcu ru dra'i chags rnams bsgral byas nas //
NK005(ca)013:2030: sha chen lang ling rkang gi dum bu dang //
NK005(ca)013:2031: zhing gi ras ros dur khrod rdzas chen rnams //
NK005(ca)013:2032: dpal gyi gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor bskor bar bya //
NK005(ca)013:2033: srid pa gsum gyi gdug pa kun bsgral te //
NK005(ca)013:2034: shes rab zab mo yum gyi mkha' dbyings su //
NK005(ca)013:2035: mtha' dang dbus med dkyil 'khor rang bzhin te //
NK005(ca)013:2036: phyi nang med par lhun gyis grub pa'i rdzas //
NK005(ca)013:2037: yid bzhin longs spyod 'dod dgu 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NK005(ca)013:2038: ye shes chen po bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags //
NK005(ca)013:2039: phrag dog rnam spangs zhing gi g.yang gzhi 'di //
NK005(ca)013:2040: dkyil 'khor chen po bla brer dgram par bya //
NK005(ca)013:2041: mchog phur bzhi dang lcags phur bzhi //
NK005(ca)013:2042: phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhir gzug pa dang //
NK005(ca)013:2043: mtha' ma rtsang gis srin mo'i 'gros //
NK005(ca)013:2044: ba su ta yi zhags pas bskor //
NK005(ca)013:2045: dpal bshos zla gam rak+ta yi //
NK005(ca)013:2046: thig le dgu pa 'bul ba dang //
NK005(ca)013:2047: rmad du byung ba'i gtor ma dang //
NK005(ca)013:2048: dmar gyi ar+g+ham chen po dang //
NK005(ca)013:2049: 'chi med bdud rtsi'i bum pa dang //
NK005(ca)013:2050: mchod pa rnam pa lnga po dang //
NK005(ca)013:2051: zab mo mchog gi tshe zan dang //
NK005(ca)013:2052: mda' dang dar sna rgyal mtshan gyis //
NK005(ca)013:2053: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor mtha' ma bskor //
NK005(ca)013:2054: mdzes rgyan mchod pa'i rten bzhugs gsol //
NK005(ca)013:2059: rol mo'i bye brag la sogs pa nye bar mkho ba'i yo byad rnams dang /
NK005(ca)013:2060: dkyil 'khor gyi byang shar du thod ngan nam hom
NK005(ca)013:2061: khung nang nyu le'i ling+ga bcug pa'i khar dur rdo
NK005(ca)013:2062: la ri gling bris pas bcad /
NK005(ca)013:2068: rang gi mdun la sogs dkyil 'khor gyi nub phyogs
NK005(ca)013:2069: su mig gi dbang po la brten nas sems kyi
NK005(ca)013:2070: ting 'dzin gsal ba sogs kyi slad du dpal chen
NK005(ca)013:2071: po gtso 'khor dgu'i sku brnyan mtshan nyid dang ldan
NK005(ca)013:2072: pa 'bur ram ri mor bris pa bzhugs su gsol
NK005(ca)013:2073: bar bya'o // rtsa ba'i bzhi pa thams cad byin gyis brlabs pa'i phrin las la lnga /
NK005(ca)013:2074: mnyam pa nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis chos thams
NK005(ca)013:2075: cad gnyis su med par byin gyis brlab pa dang
NK005(ca)013:2076: / dbang sgyur thabs kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis gnas byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK005(ca)013:2077: shes rab dang snying rje'i ting nge 'dzin gyis yum
NK005(ca)013:2078: dang rgyu dang sgrub rdzas byin gyis brlab pa dang
NK005(ca)013:2079: / phyag rgya chen po'i ting nge 'dzin gyis sgrub pa po byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK005(ca)013:2080: tshogs chen rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis rdzas dang yo byad byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK005(ca)013:2082: de'ang byin gyis rlob pa po gtso bo rdo rje slob dpon yin cing /
NK005(ca)013:2083: sgrub pa dbu tshugs nas nam grub kyi bar du
NK005(ca)013:2084: de nyid kyi dgongs pa gzhan du mi g.yel ba
NK005(ca)013:2085: dgos kyang / da lta dus dang bstan pa'i mos
NK005(ca)013:2086: slob 'dra 'bag gi skabs su 'di dag gi don
NK005(ca)013:2087: yid la gsal 'debs pa'i phyir tshig ngag tu brjod
NK005(ca)013:2088: cing rgyud gzhung gi dgongs pa ma chad na legs
NK005(ca)013:2090: chos thams cad sems nyid stong pa 'od gsal ba'i
NK005(ca)013:2091: dgos kyang / pas 'di ltar / rang bzhin no
NK005(ca)013:2092: // chos nyid ci'ang ma yin pa las ci'ang snang
NK005(ca)013:2093: ba'i cho 'phrul yi ge h'u mthing ga las 'od
NK005(ca)013:2095: tshur 'dus pa las rdo rje sngon po rtse lnga par gyur /
NK005(ca)013:2096: de las 'od zer spro bsdus 'od kyi gong bur gyur /
NK005(ca)013:2097: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)013:2098: bdag nyid dpal chen badz+ra he ru ka mthing nag zhal gsum phyag drug pa /
NK005(ca)013:2099: dpal dang dur khrod chas kyis brgyan cing yum kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai ma dang 'khril ba'o //
NK005(ca)013:2100: +aahmh'u gis sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs /
NK005(ca)013:2102: zhes ye shes lngas dbang bskur /
NK005(ca)013:2103: badz+ra sa m+aa dzah dzahmh'u bam hoh mi dmigs chos la blo brtags shing //
NK005(ca)013:2104: ye shes can gyis byin stobs kyis //
NK005(ca)013:2105: thams cad tshul bzhin byin gyis brlabs //
NK005(ca)013:2106: nus mthu can du de dag gyur //
NK005(ca)013:2109: rang gi thugs ka nas ye shes kyi rang rtsal
NK005(ca)013:2110: ram yam kham 'phros te snod kyi dngos po bsregs
NK005(ca)013:2111: gtor bkrus / a chos thams cad stong pa nyid do //
NK005(ca)013:2112: slar yang ye shes kyi 'od zer bcud kyi sems
NK005(ca)013:2113: can rnams la phog pas nyon mongs bag chags dang
NK005(ca)013:2115: de dag tshur 'dus te rang dang gnyis su med pa ye shes kyi skur gyur /
NK005(ca)013:2116: slar bdag gi thugs ka nas e yam ram bam
NK005(ca)013:2117: kem ram b+h+r+aum rnams 'phros pa'i 'od kyis snyigs ma'i
NK005(ca)013:2119: dwangs ma'i 'byung ba rim brtsegs yum lnga'i mkha' klong du gsal ba ni /
NK005(ca)013:2120: e las nam mkha'i chos 'byung gru gsum /
NK005(ca)013:2121: yam las rlung dkyil rgya gram /
NK005(ca)013:2123: bam las zhing chen gyi sa gzhi /
NK005(ca)013:2124: kem las keng rus kyi ri rab /
NK005(ca)013:2125: ram las me phung dmar nag 'bar ba'i dbus su
NK005(ca)013:2126: b+h+r+aum las ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin dur khrod rol
NK005(ca)013:2127: pa'i gzhal yas khang zla gam dbang gi dkyil 'khor
NK005(ca)013:2128: dang gnyis su med par gyur /
NK005(ca)013:2129: mtheb mdzub zlum por sprad pa'i bar srin lag gnyis bsnol te bcug /
NK005(ca)013:2130: gung mo mathe'u chung rtse sprad pa kha'i tshul du ste thod rlon gyi phyag rgya bcas la /
NK005(ca)013:2131: chos mkha' yid bzhin 'jigs byed gnas //
NK005(ca)013:2133: rnal 'byor bag yangs bsgrub byin rlabs //
NK005(ca)013:2134: dbang bsgyur chen po 'grub gyur cig /
NK005(ca)013:2135: b+h+r+aum ka p+aa la dz+ny+aa na b+h+r+aum /
NK005(ca)013:2137: thog mar yum la brten nas sbyor mchod byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK005(ca)013:2138: gzungs ma dngos su yod na de'am med na der
NK005(ca)013:2139: btags pa'i gzugs brnyan tsam la dmigs rten byas te
NK005(ca)013:2143: de kho na bde ba bzhi sbyor gyi dgongs pa gsal gdab la /
NK005(ca)013:2144: shin tu 'gying ba'i dpa' bo sgeg pa dang //
NK005(ca)013:2145: bkra shis mtshan ldan mi mos brgyan pa gnyis //
NK005(ca)013:2146: dpa' bo dgyes pa'i sbyor mchod bde ba yang //
NK005(ca)013:2147: skal ldan rnams la 'bul lo rab sprul cig /
NK005(ca)013:2148: shes rab dbyings ma yum gyi gzhal yas su //
NK005(ca)013:2149: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus mchog bkod de //
NK005(ca)013:2150: thabs dang shes rab ldan pa'i sbyor mchod kyis //
NK005(ca)013:2151: 'phags pa thams cad mnyes pa'i mchod pa 'bul //
NK005(ca)013:2152: mnyam nyid dbyings su rtogs pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK005(ca)013:2153: bde mchog longs spyod rdzogs pa sku yi rgyan //
NK005(ca)013:2154: 'dod dgu'i yon tan mdzes pas rab brgyan pa //
NK005(ca)013:2155: rnal 'byor ye shes rgyan du bzhes su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:2156: a nut+ta ra p+au dza me g+ha s+pha ra i mam ga ga na kham h'u phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)013:2157: rgyu mchog bam la brten nas bsgral ba'i dgongs pa'i byin gyis rlob pa ni /
NK005(ca)013:2158: dngos lag tu mi lon pas sgrol mchod ngo bo
NK005(ca)013:2159: tsam dkyus su 'byung bas skabs 'dir ma byas kyang
NK005(ca)013:2161: sgrub rdzas byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK005(ca)013:2162: bdag gi thugs ka nas h'u dang ha brgyad 'phros /
NK005(ca)013:2163: thod pa dang mar me rnams la thim /
NK005(ca)013:2165: gtso bo'i rten h'u dang gzhan rnams ha yig brgyad du gyur /
NK005(ca)013:2167: de dag las 'od zer spro bsdus don gnyis byas te so so'i phyag mtshan du gyur /
NK005(ca)013:2169: de las kyang 'od zer 'phro 'dus sku yongs rdzogs
NK005(ca)013:2170: su gsal ba'i gnas gsum 'bru gsum gyis mtshan par
NK005(ca)013:2171: gyur / g.yon gyi mdzub mo bkug pa la g.yas kyi mdzub mo gtad /
NK005(ca)013:2172: g.yon pa'i mtheb chen g.yas kyi mdzub mo'i rtsa bar gtad /
NK005(ca)013:2174: srin lag mathe'u chung bsnol ba phrin las bzhi'i rgya bcas la /
NK005(ca)013:2176: ban+d+ha bde gshegs sku yi sku //
NK005(ca)013:2177: yig 'bru bde gshegs gsung gi gsung //
NK005(ca)013:2178: mar me bde gshegs thugs kyi thugs //
NK005(ca)013:2179: don gyi lha dgu tshang ba yang //
NK005(ca)013:2180: don gyi lha ni brgya rtsa brgyad //
NK005(ca)013:2181: gting mtha' med pa'i skye 'gro rnams //
NK005(ca)013:2182: sangs rgyas sa la dgongs su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:2183: he ru ka kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai ha ha b+h+yo /
NK005(ca)013:2185: kong bu chos dbyings yum gyi mkha' //
NK005(ca)013:2186: mar me ye shes yab kyi 'od //
NK005(ca)013:2187: sku gsum 'gro ba'i don yang mdzad //
NK005(ca)013:2188: chos kyi dbyings kyi gzhal yas nas //
NK005(ca)013:2189: ye shes chen po sku gsum gyis //
NK005(ca)013:2190: 'khor ba'i ma rig mun bsal nas //
NK005(ca)013:2191: 'khor lo tshogs chen sa la gnas //
NK005(ca)013:2192: +aa lo ke dz+wa la d+ai pa h'u h'u /
NK005(ca)013:2194: bzhi pa gsang 'grel las don dgur gsungs kyang kha
NK005(ca)013:2195: cig bsre bsnan skabs su song ba la don gyis
NK005(ca)013:2196: tshang bas 'dir zor yang ba'i slad thog mar sgrub
NK005(ca)013:2197: pa po rnams byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK005(ca)013:2198: rang rang gi yi dam gyi lhar bsgom pa yin
NK005(ca)013:2199: kyang tshogs sgrub spyi tsam du slob dpon gyis 'di
NK005(ca)013:2200: ltar brlab ste / bdag nyid dpal chen po yab
NK005(ca)013:2201: yum du gsal ba'i thugs ka'i 'od kyis mched lcam
NK005(ca)013:2203: sbyor mtshams nas ha brgyad 'phros pa de dag gi gnas su 'khod pa phyag mtshan du gyur /
NK005(ca)013:2204: de yongs su gyur pa las ma mo chen mo
NK005(ca)013:2205: brgyad sprul pa yang sprul dang bcas pa'i tshogs su
NK005(ca)013:2206: gsal bar gyur / rdo rje rtse lnga'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK005(ca)013:2209: skal ldan 'dus pa kun tshogs nas //
NK005(ca)013:2210: gtso bo yab yum skur bskyed de //
NK005(ca)013:2211: byin rlabs cho ga kun rdzogs nas //
NK005(ca)013:2212: khro bo'i rgyal po ji bzhin bskyed //
NK005(ca)013:2214: gsang ba sgrub pa'i mched lcam rnams //
NK005(ca)013:2215: phyag rgya chen por rdzogs gyur cig /
NK005(ca)013:2217: de nas sgo dbye ba ni mched rnams mgrin gcig tu /
NK005(ca)013:2219: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK005(ca)013:2220: ma tram bsgral ba'i khog pa la //
NK005(ca)013:2221: smug nag zla gam gzhal yas shar //
NK005(ca)013:2222: phrin las rnam bzhi rdzogs mdzad pa //
NK005(ca)013:2223: shar lho nub byang phyogs bzhi nas //
NK005(ca)013:2224: ye shes chen po'i sgo phyes shig /
NK005(ca)013:2225: dzahmh'u bam hoh pra be sha ya phata /
NK005(ca)013:2228: skye med gdod nas dag pa'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK005(ca)013:2229: shes rab rang snang 'od kyi thugs rjer shar //
NK005(ca)013:2230: ye shes thabs la mkhas pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK005(ca)013:2231: gar gyi dbang phyug chen por byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK005(ca)013:2232: a la la hoh phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK005(ca)013:2234: gsang sngags yang dag zab mo'i zhing //
NK005(ca)013:2235: khro bo'i tshogs chen dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)013:2236: lha dang slob dpon blo ldan la //
NK005(ca)013:2237: brda dang gar gyis phyag bagyi'o //
NK005(ca)013:2238: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)013:2239: skabs 'dir theg pa 'og ma las lhag pa'i rtags
NK005(ca)013:2240: brgyad gdab ste sgrub pa po thabs shes zung du
NK005(ca)013:2241: 'brel ba rnams dpal he ru ka dang rjes su
NK005(ca)013:2242: mthun par bya bar gsungs pas /
NK005(ca)013:2243: chas drug dngos sam ri mor bris pa sogs dang /
NK005(ca)013:2244: rtags gsum dngos b+han+d+ha'i snod du sbyar la /
NK005(ca)013:2245: thog mar rdo rje slob dpon la rtags brgyad phul
NK005(ca)013:2246: ba ni rdo rje las pas dbyangs dang bcas glang
NK005(ca)013:2247: chen ko rlon sku stod du phul la /
NK005(ca)013:2249: gti mug rnam dag stobs bcus bdud dpung 'joms //
NK005(ca)013:2250: glang ko rnal 'byor dbang phyug rgyan du gsol //
NK005(ca)013:2251: kro d+ha ni la ka a b+hi shiny+tsa ma h+aa +aah zhing lpags stod du gsol la /
NK005(ca)013:2253: 'dod chags rnam dag yum lnga'i tshul khrims gos //
NK005(ca)013:2254: zhing g.yang rnal 'byor dbang phyug stod du gsol //
NK005(ca)013:2255: kro d+ha ni la ka sogs sngags brjod /
NK005(ca)013:2256: stag lpags sham thabs phul la /
NK005(ca)013:2258: nga rgyal rnam dag dpa' brtul dbyings su za //
NK005(ca)013:2259: stag sham rnal 'byor dbang phyug smad du gsol //
NK005(ca)013:2261: sbrul chun rigs lnga gnas so sor phul la /
NK005(ca)013:2262: zhe sdang rnam dag dpa' brjid mnyen la lcugs //
NK005(ca)013:2263: sbrul chun rnal 'byor dbang phyug rgyan du 'bul //
NK005(ca)013:2267: rlon pa'i do shal phul la /
NK005(ca)013:2269: phrag dog rnam dag dbang chen gsum po brnyes //
NK005(ca)013:2270: thod pa tshar gsum sku yi rgyan du bzhes //
NK005(ca)013:2272: khrag chen gyi theg le mkhur tshos gnyis su phul la /
NK005(ca)013:2274: thugs rje chags pas pad can sa mnan phyir //
NK005(ca)013:2275: rak+ta'i thig le don mdzad rtags su bzhes //
NK005(ca)013:2277: thal chen tshom bu gsum dpral bar btab la /
NK005(ca)013:2279: gdug pa kun 'dul tshogs chen sa mnan phyir //
NK005(ca)013:2280: thal chen tshon bu brjid pa'i rtags su bzhes //
NK005(ca)013:2282: zhag gi zo ris zhal gyi grwa gnyis su bkod la /
NK005(ca)013:2284: don dam bcu 'bar kun 'ong sa mnan phyir //
NK005(ca)013:2285: zhag gi zo ris byang sems rtags su bzhes //
NK005(ca)013:2287: de nas slob dpon gyis mched rnams la rtags gsum rim par gdab cing byin gyis brlab ste /
NK005(ca)013:2289: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK005(ca)013:2290: dur khrod sa brgyad mnan pa dang //
NK005(ca)013:2291: rdzu 'phrul thabs kyis sgrub pa dang //
NK005(ca)013:2292: dpal chen thabs kyis bsdu bar bya //
NK005(ca)013:2293: he ru ka dang gcig pa'i phyir //
NK005(ca)013:2294: thal ba'i thig les mtshan pa 'di //
NK005(ca)013:2295: 'di yang sngon gyi tha tshig la //
NK005(ca)013:2296: 'di yang rtags kyi phyag rgya ste //
NK005(ca)013:2297: 'di yang bdag nyid chen po'i rgya'o //
NK005(ca)013:2298: sarba ta th+aa ga ta badz+ra garba s+t+wam pa si hoh mkha' 'gro kun dang gcig pa'i phyir //
NK005(ca)013:2300: 'di yang sngon gyi tha tshig la //
NK005(ca)013:2301: 'di yang rtags kyi phyag rgya ste //
NK005(ca)013:2302: 'di yang bdag nyid chen po'i rgya'o //
NK005(ca)013:2303: sarba ta th+aa ga ta rak+ta si hoh ging chen kun dang gcig pa'i phyir //
NK005(ca)013:2304: zhag gi zo ris mtshan pa 'di //
NK005(ca)013:2305: 'di yang sngon gyi 'di yang rtags kyi 'di yang
NK005(ca)013:2306: bdag nyid na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta s+t+wam pa
NK005(ca)013:2308: de nas dam bca' ba ni slob dpon gyis /
NK005(ca)013:2310: dam pa 'du 'bral med pa'i gzungs thag la //
NK005(ca)013:2311: rig pa srog gis bsdus pa'i lu gu rgyud //
NK005(ca)013:2312: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK005(ca)013:2313: skye ba ji srid bar du ma gtong zhig /
NK005(ca)013:2315: mched lcam rnams kyis de nyid kyi tshig rkang bzhi pa'i mtha' /
NK005(ca)013:2318: de nas byin dbab pa ni /
NK005(ca)013:2319: sgrub pa po rnams chas kyis brgyan /
NK005(ca)013:2320: pho rnams mchog gi hasta dar gyis brgyan pa dang /
NK005(ca)013:2321: mo rnams kyis phreng ba g.yab /
NK005(ca)013:2322: tshil chen gyi dud pa dang rol mo gdung dbyangs bshugs glu'i sgra rnams kyis bskul bas /
NK005(ca)013:2323: brgyud gsum rig 'dzin bla ma rnams dang /
NK005(ca)013:2324: dpal chen badz+ra he ru ka'i lha tshogs thams cad
NK005(ca)013:2325: nam mkha' 'gengs pa tsam du 'thibs kyis byon nas
NK005(ca)013:2326: / bdag gnas dkyil 'khor yo byad dang bcas pa
NK005(ca)013:2327: la thim pas sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan
NK005(ca)013:2328: gyis 'khor los byin gyis brlabs par mos la /
NK005(ca)013:2330: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK005(ca)013:2331: rnal 'byor dbang phyug rigs kyi yum dang bcas //
NK005(ca)013:2332: rgyal ba 'khor bcas srung ma dam tshig can //
NK005(ca)013:2333: mchod gnas bla ma rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)013:2334: bdag cag rnams ni sems can dman pa la //
NK005(ca)013:2335: gnyen bshes mthu dpung gzhan na ma mchis pas //
NK005(ca)013:2336: thugs rje chen po'i dbri bkol mi mdzad cing //
NK005(ca)013:2337: dus las mi 'da' thugs rje dam tshig can //
NK005(ca)013:2338: skyabs las mi g.yel yal gam gcig tu dgongs //
NK005(ca)013:2339: ye shes rgyas pa'i rlabs las ma g.yos kyang //
NK005(ca)013:2340: dam tshig sems nyid rab tu mngon rtogs shing //
NK005(ca)013:2341: byin rlabs chen po dus 'dir stsal du gsol //
NK005(ca)013:2342: a la la hoh b+ha ga w+aan /
NK005(ca)013:2343: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)013:2345: dkyil 'khor gzung ba'i dus la bab //
NK005(ca)013:2346: byin chen dbab pa'i dus la bab //
NK005(ca)013:2347: dbang chen bskur ba'i dus la bab //
NK005(ca)013:2348: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK005(ca)013:2349: dngos grub stsol ba'i dus la bab //
NK005(ca)013:2350: byin chen byin phob bcom ldan 'das //
NK005(ca)013:2351: dbang chen dbang bskur bcom ldan 'das //
NK005(ca)013:2352: mthu chen mthu stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK005(ca)013:2353: dngos grub mchog stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK005(ca)013:2354: rtags dang mtshan ma bstan pa dang //
NK005(ca)013:2355: bdag gi bsam pa 'grub par mdzod //
NK005(ca)013:2356: a la la hoh zhes pa dang /
NK005(ca)013:2357: lha mo ko'u r+ai ma brgyad kyang gong ltar spyan drangs la byin dbab /
NK005(ca)013:2358: phud gtor la bar chad med par dngos grub 'grub pa'i phrin las bcol lo //
NK005(ca)013:2362: de dag stong nyid du byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK005(ca)013:2363: dang po la'ang spro na zhu ba dang lan gyi phrin las gdab pa ni gsang 'grel ltar ro //
NK005(ca)013:2364: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i sngags ring brjod la yungs thun gtor te bgegs bskrad /
NK005(ca)013:2365: dung phor du chu gtsang tsan+dana dkar dmar gyi phye
NK005(ca)013:2366: dang sbyar ba la khro mo dbang phyug ma'i sngags
NK005(ca)013:2367: rgyas byin rlabs spyi ltar byas la /
NK005(ca)013:2368: de'i sngags kyis bsang gtor bya zhing spos kyi dud pas kyang bsang /
NK005(ca)013:2369: bdag gi thugs ka'i h'u gi 'od zer gyis yo
NK005(ca)013:2370: byad dngos 'dzin gyi rnam par rtog pa sbyangs nas
NK005(ca)013:2372: de'i ngang las snod thams cad b+h+r+aum las rin po
NK005(ca)013:2373: che'i gzhal yas khang gi nang du ma las nyi
NK005(ca)013:2375: bcud thams cad a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor du
NK005(ca)013:2376: gyur pa'i dbus su dmar po las 'od zer phyogs
NK005(ca)013:2377: bcur 'phros / snod bcud kyi bdud rtsi thams cad
NK005(ca)013:2378: zla ba la bsdus pas bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho dkar
NK005(ca)013:2379: bcur 'phros / ltem gyi gyur / de'i dbus su
NK005(ca)013:2380: dkar po'i 'od zer gyis 'dod yon drug gi lha
NK005(ca)013:2381: mo re re las kyang dpag tu med pa 'phel
NK005(ca)013:2382: te nam mkha'i khams dang mnyam par gyur /
NK005(ca)013:2384: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK005(ca)013:2385: nyon mongs dug sel yid bzhin bdud rtsi'i mchog /
NK005(ca)013:2386: chos nyid dag pas rigs lnga'i dam tshig lnga //
NK005(ca)013:2387: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK005(ca)013:2388: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan pa //
NK005(ca)013:2389: thugs dam bzhin du ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:2392: zhes sgrub pa'i mthun rkyen gyi yo byad spyi 'dod
NK005(ca)013:2393: pa'i yon tan lnga'i mchod sprin chen por byin brlab
NK005(ca)013:2394: / gnyis pa la thog mar dza gad ni /
NK005(ca)013:2395: b+han+d+ha la sogs pa'i snod chang gis bkang ba slob dpon gyi mdun du bzhag la /
NK005(ca)013:2396: dza gad kyi snod b+h+r+aum las rin po che'i gzhal
NK005(ca)013:2397: yas khang gi nang du ma las nyi ma'i dkyil
NK005(ca)013:2398: 'khor / de'i steng du h'u sngon po'i 'od zer gyis tha mal gyi dngos po sbyangs te /
NK005(ca)013:2399: h'u de nyid bcom ldan 'das mi bskyod pa sngon po sa gnon mnyam bzhag can /
NK005(ca)013:2400: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa'i skur gyur /
NK005(ca)013:2402: phyag rgya las yum spyan ma dkar mo rigs lngas
NK005(ca)013:2403: dbu brgyan pa zhig 'phros te 'khril sbyor gyi mchod
NK005(ca)013:2404: pas mnyes nas / byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin
NK005(ca)013:2405: mu tig dkar po dri ma med pa ltar zhu
NK005(ca)013:2406: ste snod gang zhing 'phel bar gyur /
NK005(ca)013:2407: de'i dbus su nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng yi
NK005(ca)013:2408: ge m+aam las yum m+aa ma k+ai dkar mo bdud
NK005(ca)013:2410: de las sprul pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'phros
NK005(ca)013:2411: te 'jig rten khams kyi bdud rtsi chu'i bcud thams
NK005(ca)013:2412: cad bsdus te thim pas thams cad 'od du zhu
NK005(ca)013:2413: ba byang sems bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin du gyur /
NK005(ca)013:2414: ma ma ki ri ki ri a d+hish+tha swa mam /
NK005(ca)013:2415: zhes brjod la byin gyis brlabs pa'i chang des phyin chad kyi mchod pa'i phud dang /
NK005(ca)013:2416: tshogs chang sogs sgrub pa po'i btung ba thams cad la khyab par basre'o //
NK005(ca)013:2417: de nas bdud rtsi byin rlabs las byang ltar bya'o //
NK005(ca)013:2419: gtor gzhong b+h+r+aum las zla gam dmar po dbang gi
NK005(ca)013:2420: gzhal yas khang du gyur pa'i nang du pad nyi
NK005(ca)013:2421: dregs pa bam ro'i gdan la /
NK005(ca)013:2422: bdag gi thugs ka nas h'u dang ha brgyad spros /
NK005(ca)013:2426: zhes brjod pas dpal chen po badz+ra he ru ka
NK005(ca)013:2427: 'khor goo r+ai lha mo brgyad dang bcas pa lhag
NK005(ca)013:2428: ger gsal ba'i dpal gyi pho brang chen por gyur
NK005(ca)013:2432: phyi mchod byin rlabs rnams las byang ltar btang ba'i rjes su /
NK005(ca)013:2433: gzhan yang thabs tshul mtha' yas pa'i //
NK005(ca)013:2434: mchod sprin bla med phyogs bcur 'bul //
NK005(ca)013:2435: nam mkha' mdzod kyi gter la sogs //
NK005(ca)013:2436: bla med mchod sprin rab 'byams rnams //
NK005(ca)013:2437: dad pas dmigs te 'bul lags kyi //
NK005(ca)013:2438: sngon gyi thugs dam dgyes dgongs te //
NK005(ca)013:2439: dkyil 'khor rgyan du bzhes su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:2440: p+au dza me g+ha sa mu dra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h'u /
NK005(ca)013:2443: don dam par chos thams cad stong pa nyid du
NK005(ca)013:2444: rtogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin dngos sam mos sgom gyi
NK005(ca)013:2445: rgyas 'debs thog mtha' kun tu bya'o //
NK005(ca)013:2447: slob ma rnams sngar dbang ma thob na skabs 'dir
NK005(ca)013:2448: phyi nang gsang ba rdzogs pa'i dbang bzhis smin par
NK005(ca)013:2450: deng sang sa bon sngon song gi dbang du btang ste 'dir mi mdzad pa shas che la /
NK005(ca)013:2451: dgos shing spro na dbang chog las rtogs par bya'o //
NK005(ca)013:2452: rtsa ba'i drug pa lha mnyes par bya ba'i phrin las ni /
NK005(ca)013:2453: rtsa ba'i gzhung las don lngas bstan kyang deng sang
NK005(ca)013:2454: 'dul ba yul chos su sbyor ba'i dbang du byas
NK005(ca)013:2455: te / dngos gzhi'i nyin dang po nas brtsam sgrub zhag tu byed kun la 'dra bar brgyud 'debs /
NK005(ca)013:2456: yan lag brgyad pas rgyud sbyong ba nas mchod pa
NK005(ca)013:2457: byin rlabs rdzogs kyi bar las kyi sngon 'gro rnams
NK005(ca)013:2458: dang / dngos gzhi ting nge 'dzin gsum gyis khog dbub /
NK005(ca)013:2459: rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor bdag mdun dbyer med du bskyed /
NK005(ca)013:2460: las kyi rim pa'i ting 'dzin ye shes pa spyan
NK005(ca)013:2461: drangs pa nas bzhugs gsol phyag mchod bstod pa yan
NK005(ca)013:2462: las byang gi dkyus su bstan pa ltar mthar chags
NK005(ca)013:2463: su bya / de nas 'dzab bsnyen 'bul ba'i phrin las la gnyis /
NK005(ca)013:2468: 'bru brgyad kyi bzlas thabs dngos so //
NK005(ca)013:2471: bsnyen pa la shub bur bzlas pa /
NK005(ca)013:2472: sgrub pa la dbyangs su len pa /
NK005(ca)013:2473: las sbyor gyi skabs drag por brjod pa ste bzla
NK005(ca)013:2474: tshul man ngag bzhir bshad pa'i skabs 'dir gsum pa
NK005(ca)013:2475: nyid gtso bor gyur pa ste /
NK005(ca)013:2476: de'ang rgyud gal po las gsungs pa'i dbyangs drug po blang thabs /
NK005(ca)013:2478: yon tan gsum gsum gyi sgo nas so so'i skabs
NK005(ca)013:2479: dang sbyar la 'dren pa'i tshul brgyud ldan gong ma
NK005(ca)013:2480: rnams kyi gsung rgyun las rtogs par bya dgos shing
NK005(ca)013:2481: / de'i thog ma sngar gyi yi ge sgra sgrogs pa'i dbyangs nyid kun la gces pa ste /
NK005(ca)013:2482: ngag ha cang mi myur mi dal ha cang sgra mi che mi chung /
NK005(ca)013:2483: ngag gzhan dang mi smra zhing sems gzhan du mi g.yeng /
NK005(ca)013:2484: gug skyed tshigs zur mi nyams par bzla ba'o //
NK005(ca)013:2489: dbye gzhi'i dkyil 'khor gsal btab nas sngags kyis bskul
NK005(ca)013:2490: bas ye shes kyi 'khor lo rten dang brten par
NK005(ca)013:2491: bcas pa logs su phyes te mdun dkyil sgrub rdzas
NK005(ca)013:2492: dang dbyer med du bzhugs par mos /
NK005(ca)013:2494: spyir ru lu yon tan du shes pa dang /
NK005(ca)013:2495: bye brag shes pa brgyad ldan gyis bzla ba'o //
NK005(ca)013:2499: kun tu bzang po he ru ka /
NK005(ca)013:2500: dpal be'u thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ni //
NK005(ca)013:2501: ye shes snying po 'bru brgyad ldan //
NK005(ca)013:2502: ni sku dang ye shes nyid //
NK005(ca)013:2503: dpal chen 'bar ba seng ges brjid //
NK005(ca)013:2504: ru lu ma mo nam mkha' 'phro //
NK005(ca)013:2505: ma tshogs sprin dang skar ltar 'phro //
NK005(ca)013:2506: h'u chen nyi zla'i tshogs rgyun 'dra //
NK005(ca)013:2507: ma nor re skong mkha' la 'gro //
NK005(ca)013:2508: sngags kyi yon tan khyad par 'phags //
NK005(ca)013:2509: ru lu 'di ni sgrib pa sbyang //
NK005(ca)013:2510: las dang nyon mongs bag chags 'joms //
NK005(ca)013:2511: ru lu 'di ni rtogs pa skye //
NK005(ca)013:2512: sgom nyams sems la rnam par 'phel //
NK005(ca)013:2513: ru lu 'di ni ya mtshan che //
NK005(ca)013:2514: bdud dang mu stegs ru dra 'dul //
NK005(ca)013:2515: ru lu 'di ni dngos grub thob //
NK005(ca)013:2516: mchog thun myur du 'grub byed pa'o //
NK005(ca)013:2517: zhes pas bskul zhing gsal btab la 'bru brgyad dbyangs su blang ngo //
NK005(ca)013:2519: dkyil 'khor lha dang bzlas brjod las /
NK005(ca)013:2520: mchod bshags dngos grub chos nyid do //
NK005(ca)013:2521: de la dang po dkyil 'khor du shes pa la'ang gsum du gsungs te /
NK005(ca)013:2522: phyi snod dur khrod chen po'i gzhal yas khang du gsal gdab pa ni /
NK005(ca)013:2524: dbang chen yum lnga 'dus pa'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK005(ca)013:2525: ma tram ru dra bsgral ba'i khog pa la //
NK005(ca)013:2526: b+han+d+ha tshar gsum brtsegs pa'i brtsigs pa byas //
NK005(ca)013:2527: rak+ta'i spyin sbyar gnam lcags gzer chen btab //
NK005(ca)013:2528: yon tan che rgyas gru bzhi mchod rten tshul //
NK005(ca)013:2529: zla gam dbang mtshon smug nag 'bar ba na //
NK005(ca)013:2530: ka ba mchog brgyad ldan pa'i re'u cha dgu //
NK005(ca)013:2531: tshangs pa'i gdung bzhi mchog chen ka ba dang //
NK005(ca)013:2532: nyi zla'i ka gzhu bam chen ka gdan dang //
NK005(ca)013:2533: sbrul gyi skyes bu ka ru'i ya lcib la //
NK005(ca)013:2534: rus sbal ma them zhing gi sgo glegs te //
NK005(ca)013:2535: t+aa la'i skyes shing 'dod yon lha mos gang //
NK005(ca)013:2536: 'bar ba'i bar khyams dur khrod gnas bcas te //
NK005(ca)013:2537: rab 'jigs dur khrod chen po'i rgyan dang chas //
NK005(ca)013:2538: mtha' dang dbus med ye shes nam mkha'i rgya //
NK005(ca)013:2539: dregs pa khyo shugs bsnol zhing zhing chen bting //
NK005(ca)013:2540: rab gsal nyi ma'i gdan dang bcas pa 'di //
NK005(ca)013:2541: rgyu 'bras ma bkag dag pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK005(ca)013:2542: dpal chen khrag 'thung tshogs kyi bzhugs gnas so //
NK005(ca)013:2544: nang bcud khrag 'thung phyag rgya'i tshogs su gsal gdab pa ni /
NK005(ca)013:2546: chos nyid skye med gdod nas dag pa las //
NK005(ca)013:2547: skye ba'i cho 'phrul 'bar ba'i skur bstan pa'i //
NK005(ca)013:2548: bcom ldan dpal chen khrag 'thung yab yum la //
NK005(ca)013:2549: ke'u seng la sogs mkha' 'gro'i tshogs kyis bskor //
NK005(ca)013:2550: ye shes skur gsal thugs rjes khyab pa'i sku //
NK005(ca)013:2551: gdug pa 'dul phyir 'jigs byed skur ston pa //
NK005(ca)013:2552: dur khrod rgyan mdzes gdug byed mtshon cha bsnams //
NK005(ca)013:2553: bskal pa'i me 'bar dur khrod dkyil 'khor na //
NK005(ca)013:2554: khams gsum stong mdzad khrag 'thung phyag rgya'i tshogs //
NK005(ca)013:2555: rgyu 'bras ma 'gag lha yi dkyil 'khor gsal //
NK005(ca)013:2557: gsang ba de dag kyang byang chub sems su gsal gdab pa ni /
NK005(ca)013:2559: phyi nang snod bcud chos nyid chen po ni //
NK005(ca)013:2560: rang bzhin rnam dag sems kyi spyod yul la //
NK005(ca)013:2561: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis su ngas ma mthong //
NK005(ca)013:2562: snang stong dbyer med rdo rje theg pa'i lam //
NK005(ca)013:2563: go ba'i yul 'di sangs rgyas bde ba'i zhing //
NK005(ca)013:2564: 'di nyid rnam dag sprul sku thug 'phrad gsal //
NK005(ca)013:2566: gnyis pa lhar shes pa la gnyis kyi /
NK005(ca)013:2567: spyi'i dbang du sbyar ba ni /
NK005(ca)013:2568: ni dpal chen sku gsung thugs //
NK005(ca)013:2569: ru lu gnas yul phyag rgya brgyad //
NK005(ca)013:2570: h'u ni thabs shes sgo ma bzhi //
NK005(ca)013:2571: b+h+yo ni ma sring rgya mtsho'i tshogs //
NK005(ca)013:2572: h'u ni ye shes sems dpa'i sku //
NK005(ca)013:2573: zur brgyad steng na 'bru brgyad gsal //
NK005(ca)013:2575: gsal bar bsgom zhing gsal bar brtag /
NK005(ca)013:2576: brtags pas 'bru brgyad lha rnams gsal //
NK005(ca)013:2578: khyad par gyi dbang du sbyar ba ni /
NK005(ca)013:2579: ni dkar mo ke'u r+ai ma //
NK005(ca)013:2580: ru ni rkun mo tso'u r+ai ma //
NK005(ca)013:2581: lu mi sbos mo pra mo h+aa //
NK005(ca)013:2582: ru ni thal byed be ta l+ai //
NK005(ca)013:2583: lu ni rgan byed puk+ka s+ai //
NK005(ca)013:2584: h'u ni gtum mo gasma r+ai //
NK005(ca)013:2585: b+h+yo ni sme sha sma sha n+ai //
NK005(ca)013:2586: h'u ni ma tshogs tsan d+ha l+ai //
NK005(ca)013:2587: kun bsdus dpal chen snying po ste //
NK005(ca)013:2588: yang dag don gyi lha dgur gsal //
NK005(ca)013:2590: gsum pa bzlas brjod du shes pa la 'phro 'du
NK005(ca)013:2591: gsum yod pa'i dang po spro bsdu'i gzhi gsal gdab
NK005(ca)013:2592: pa ni / bdag mdun gtso bo'i tsit+ta rin po
NK005(ca)013:2593: che'i gzhal yas khang zla gam sgo gcig pa'i nang
NK005(ca)013:2594: du nyi zla brtsegs pa'i gdan la ye shes sems
NK005(ca)013:2595: dpa' smug nag tshon gang ba /
NK005(ca)013:2596: de'i thugs kar zla ba'i steng du rin po che
NK005(ca)013:2597: zur brgyad pa'i nang du phyed nub tsam gyi rdo
NK005(ca)013:2598: rje rtse dgu pa'i lte bar h'u yig sngon po
NK005(ca)013:2599: 'bar ba / rin po che zur brgyad kyi rtse
NK005(ca)013:2600: la ru lu 'bru brgyad ljang dmar spus bris pa
NK005(ca)013:2601: tsam bklag phyogs su 'khor zhing 'od zer 'phro ba
NK005(ca)013:2602: 'bar ba / / lce rdo rje rtse gsum pa'i
NK005(ca)013:2603: rtse mor pad+ma'i lte bar la ru lu 'bru brgyad
NK005(ca)013:2604: 'bar ba / / kyis bskor ba / de dag
NK005(ca)013:2605: kyang mar me ltar 'bar zhing gsal ba'i 'od zer
NK005(ca)013:2607: / ma mo brgyad kyi thugs kar b+hany+dza til 'bru
NK005(ca)013:2609: re re'i mtha' yang ru lu 'bru brgyad kyis bskor ba /
NK005(ca)013:2610: h'u gi rang sgras 'bru brgyad la bskul bas de
NK005(ca)013:2611: las yig 'bru ljang dmar nyi zer gyi rdul lta
NK005(ca)013:2612: bu 'phros pas / ye shes kyi lha tshogs rnams dgyes pa bskyed /
NK005(ca)013:2614: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thams cad yig 'bru'i rnam pas bdag la stsal zhing thim par gyur /
NK005(ca)013:2615: ces dmigs la sngags kyi 'phro 'du bskul ba ni /
NK005(ca)013:2616: h'u ni thabs chen shes rab sbyor //
NK005(ca)013:2617: ye shes thig le thugs la shar //
NK005(ca)013:2618: zur brgyad steng na 'bru brgyad spro //
NK005(ca)013:2619: khams gsum sems can sdug bsngal bsal //
NK005(ca)013:2620: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i sku la thim //
NK005(ca)013:2621: sngags tshig sgra yi mchod pas mnyes //
NK005(ca)013:2622: tshur 'dus dang po'i gnas su thim //
NK005(ca)013:2623: lus ngag yid gsum sgrib pa sbyangs //
NK005(ca)013:2624: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob //
NK005(ca)013:2625: gnyis su med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK005(ca)013:2629: gong gi yig 'bru'i spro bsdu de 'od zer du bsgyur la /
NK005(ca)013:2633: gsal 'tsher thogs med kun tu khyab //
NK005(ca)013:2634: phar 'phros pas ni gzhan don mdzad //
NK005(ca)013:2636: rnam par spros pas bsod nams tshogs //
NK005(ca)013:2637: stong par gsal bas ye shes tshogs //
NK005(ca)013:2638: tshogs gnyis rdzogs pas mngon 'tshang rgya //
NK005(ca)013:2641: rgyas par gtso 'khor so sor bskul ba yod kyang spyi tsam du /
NK005(ca)013:2642: bdag gi thugs ka'i sa bon sngags phreng rnams las sngags phreng 'od zer dang bcas pa byung /
NK005(ca)013:2643: ye shes sems dpa'i zhal nas brgyud /
NK005(ca)013:2644: lce steng gi sngags phreng dang 'dres te de las de 'dra ba byung /
NK005(ca)013:2645: zhal nas thon te mdun bskyed dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo'i ljags las brgyud de thugs kar zhugs /
NK005(ca)013:2646: de las 'phros pa'i sngags phreng sbyor mtshams nas thon
NK005(ca)013:2647: te rang nyid kyi sbyor mtshams nas thugs kar thim
NK005(ca)013:2648: par mos pa mgal me bskor ba'i tshul gyis ting
NK005(ca)013:2649: 'dzin rgyun ma chad par byas la //
NK005(ca)013:2650: dpal chen khrag 'thung thugs ni rin po che //
NK005(ca)013:2651: thugs rje sku mchog yid bzhin 'byung ba'i gter //
NK005(ca)013:2652: bdag ni bla med byang chub sems bskyed de //
NK005(ca)013:2653: rang sems gdod nas ma skyes rin po che //
NK005(ca)013:2654: lha dang gnyis su med par mnyam bzhag nas //
NK005(ca)013:2655: ut+pala 'dab brgyad lta bu'i ljags brkyang zhing //
NK005(ca)013:2656: khur ba dbugs ring dang bcas pa yis //
NK005(ca)013:2657: ru lu ru lu 'khor lo tshogs chen po //
NK005(ca)013:2658: bar chad med pa'i bzlas brjod ting 'dzin gyis //
NK005(ca)013:2659: sems rtog sbyong zhing dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK005(ca)013:2661: badz+ra ma h+aa sogs gtso sngags dang /
NK005(ca)013:2662: lha mo brgyad la'ang spro bsdu ji ltar rigs pa
NK005(ca)013:2663: sbyar te sgos 'dzab la ru lu sbyar pa rnams
NK005(ca)013:2664: bzla / 'dir yang gtso bo spyi 'dzab ru lu nyid ci nus bazla'o //
NK005(ca)013:2665: de ltar shes pa gsum ba de las dzapa bskul thams cad mi lcogs na /
NK005(ca)013:2666: dkyil 'khor byang sems su shes pa /
NK005(ca)013:2668: bzlas brjod yig 'bru 'od zer gcig tu bsdu ba dang /
NK005(ca)013:2669: lha la 'phro 'du bya ba rnams kyis 'thus so //
NK005(ca)013:2670: bzhi pa phrin las su shes pa ni /
NK005(ca)013:2671: sgrub pa grub la nye ba na /
NK005(ca)013:2673: zhag grangs kyi bcu cha tsam sbyor ba ste /
NK005(ca)013:2674: de la gzhung nas zhi rgyas dbang drag mnan zlog drug so sor gsungs kyang /
NK005(ca)013:2676: ru lu 'od zer rnam drug dang //
NK005(ca)013:2677: sgra dbyangs 'dren tshul rnam drug gis //
NK005(ca)013:2678: las bzhi mnan zlog 'grub par byed //
NK005(ca)013:2679: las rnams grub nas dbyings su rol //
NK005(ca)013:2680: ces bskul te gnas bzhi nas 'od zer mdog mtshungs
NK005(ca)013:2681: su spros pas phrin las thogs med du grub par
NK005(ca)013:2683: lnga pa mchod par shes pa ni /
NK005(ca)013:2684: thugs ka'i ru lu ye shes kyi 'od zer las
NK005(ca)013:2685: mchod pa rnams sprul te ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor
NK005(ca)013:2688: me tog bdug spos lha bshos mar me bcas //
NK005(ca)013:2689: bla bre rgyal mtshan na bza' 'phan dang gdugs //
NK005(ca)013:2690: sil snyan rnga dung rin chen mu tig phreng //
NK005(ca)013:2691: gzugs sgra dri ro reg sogs lha mo'i tshogs //
NK005(ca)013:2692: bde chen byang chub sems kyi mchod spran rnams //
NK005(ca)013:2693: dngos su bshams shing sems kyis rnam sprul te //
NK005(ca)013:2694: ye shes rang snang zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK005(ca)013:2695: 'bru brgyad 'phro 'dus dbus na mchod par bzhes //
NK005(ca)013:2697: drug pa bshags par shes pa ni /
NK005(ca)013:2698: 'bru brgyad ye shes kyi 'od kyis rtsa gsum srung
NK005(ca)013:2699: mar bcas pa la phog pas de dag las ye
NK005(ca)013:2700: shes kyi 'od dpag tu med pa 'phros te bdag
NK005(ca)013:2701: la thim pas sgrib gnyis bag chags dang bcas pa
NK005(ca)013:2702: byang nas stong gsal 'od phung du gyur par mos
NK005(ca)013:2703: la // ye shes lha tshogs zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK005(ca)013:2704: rig 'dzin dam can rgya mtsho dgongs su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:2705: tshe rabs thog mtha' med pa'i dbus mtha' nas //
NK005(ca)013:2706: da lta lus 'di blangs pa yan chad du //
NK005(ca)013:2707: rang sems ma rig bdag tu bzung ba yis //
NK005(ca)013:2708: 'khor ba'i nyes skyon sna tshogs byung nas su //
NK005(ca)013:2709: kun gzhi blo la bag chags bsags pa dang //
NK005(ca)013:2710: bar du thugs rjes bzung dang rtsol ba yis //
NK005(ca)013:2711: byang chub sems bskyed thar lam sgor zhugs te //
NK005(ca)013:2712: theg pa rim par bgrod cing spyad pa'i tshe //
NK005(ca)013:2713: tshul khrims sdom pa phyi nang dam tshig las //
NK005(ca)013:2714: zhig ral chag nyams gyur pa ci mchis dang //
NK005(ca)013:2715: khyad par gsang sngags theg pa'i sgor zhugs nas //
NK005(ca)013:2716: 'da' dka' sdom pa'i dam tshig mnos pa las //
NK005(ca)013:2717: sngon du spyad pa'i goms shugs chung ba yis //
NK005(ca)013:2718: nyams su ma rtogs gzhung bzhin ma spyad de //
NK005(ca)013:2719: bla ma mched la sri zhu brtse gdung chung //
NK005(ca)013:2720: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun bcad gsang tshig spel //
NK005(ca)013:2721: mdzad spyod rnams lngas 'gro don lhur ma blang //
NK005(ca)013:2722: dug lnga rnam grol lam du gnas ma gyur //
NK005(ca)013:2723: mnyam pa'i mchod pas lta ba thag ma bcad //
NK005(ca)013:2724: shes par bya ba'i spyod yul yal ba btang //
NK005(ca)013:2725: grub par bya ba'i 'bras bu rgyun thag bsrings //
NK005(ca)013:2726: dbang dang mi ldan chos bshad las rnams brtsams //
NK005(ca)013:2727: rtogs pa stobs chung dge sgom sgrub la g.yel //
NK005(ca)013:2728: dam rdzas mchod tshogs gzhung bzhin ma bstabs dang //
NK005(ca)013:2729: dam bcas khas blangs bgyis kun rjes ma sobs //
NK005(ca)013:2730: byang chub rigs can spyod pas thugs ma bsrungs //
NK005(ca)013:2731: bar chod gnod rkyen ma bzod 'khrul sems shor //
NK005(ca)013:2732: snod dang mi ldan grogs ngan grib mas phog /
NK005(ca)013:2733: de la sogs te nyes sdig ci bsags pa //
NK005(ca)013:2734: gnong 'gyod mthol bshags bzod par gsol lags na //
NK005(ca)013:2735: byams mgon thugs rjes tshangs pa stsal du gsol //
NK005(ca)013:2737: mchod bshags 'di gnyis ni bzlas brjod bzhag nas thun mtshams la 'jug ka thams bcad du bya'o //
NK005(ca)013:2738: bdun pa dngos grub shes pa ni /
NK005(ca)013:2739: bdag gi thugs ka nas ru lu 'bru brgyad ljang dmar gyi tshogs 'phros /
NK005(ca)013:2740: ye shes 'khor lo'i gnas gsum du thim nas mnyes par byas /
NK005(ca)013:2741: de'i sku gsung thugs kyi gnas nas ru lu smug nag dpag tu med pa 'phros te byung /
NK005(ca)013:2742: bdag gi gnas gsum du thim pas sku 'gyur med /
NK005(ca)013:2744: thugs skye 'chi med pa'i dngos grub thob par gyur /
NK005(ca)013:2748: sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor bsam mi khyab //
NK005(ca)013:2749: zla gam rin chen dkyil 'khor dbang //
NK005(ca)013:2750: nub phyogs ngos su kha bltas te //
NK005(ca)013:2751: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK005(ca)013:2753: tshon gang chos kyi 'khor lo las //
NK005(ca)013:2755: phar 'phros pas ni ye shes lha'i //
NK005(ca)013:2756: sku gsung thugs la mchod pa 'bul //
NK005(ca)013:2757: slar 'dus pas ni sgrub pa pos //
NK005(ca)013:2758: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob //
NK005(ca)013:2760: 'di ni sgrub pa sangs nyin grol ba'i de ring nas sbyar bar bya'o //
NK005(ca)013:2761: brgyad pa ni thun mtshams rnams dang rjes kyi bya ba ste 'og tu ston no //
NK005(ca)013:2762: gnyis pa thun mtshams kyi bya ba la /
NK005(ca)013:2763: dzapa 'bul zhing dngos grub bsdu ba /
NK005(ca)013:2764: mchod bstod kyis thugs dam bskul ba /
NK005(ca)013:2765: bar chad nyams lon 'dul zhing byin bsdu ba'o //
NK005(ca)013:2768: sngags tshig bzlas brjod sogs nas /
NK005(ca)013:2769: rig pa'i me tog dor te /
NK005(ca)013:2770: lus thams cad gang bar gyur /
NK005(ca)013:2771: ces pa'i bar las byang ltar ro //
NK005(ca)013:2772: gnyis pa la mchod pa ni /
NK005(ca)013:2775: tshogs kyi 'khor lo gsum ka'am gang yang rung ba de bya dgos pas /
NK005(ca)013:2776: dang po ltar na sbyor mchod ni /
NK005(ca)013:2777: don dbyings dang ye shes su sbyor ba'i dgongs pa gsal gdab la //
NK005(ca)013:2778: phyogs bcu'i stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK005(ca)013:2779: sna tshogs snang ba thabs kyi yab //
NK005(ca)013:2780: ma skyes pa nyid shes rab ste //
NK005(ca)013:2781: ye shes lha dang dbyer med cing //
NK005(ca)013:2782: 'bru brgyud sngags kyi yi ger gsungs //
NK005(ca)013:2783: sbros pas bla med mchod pa 'bul //
NK005(ca)013:2784: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK005(ca)013:2786: rtags rnal 'byor pa rtogs goms kyi tshod dang sbyar
NK005(ca)013:2787: ba'i rig ma gsum dang snyoms par zhugs pa'i ting
NK005(ca)013:2789: ni chos nyid chos kyi sku //
NK005(ca)013:2790: ru ni dpal chen he ru ka /
NK005(ca)013:2791: lu ni kro ti shwa r+ai yum //
NK005(ca)013:2792: ru ni dbyer med zung dang 'brel //
NK005(ca)013:2793: lu ni mi gtong 'dzin pa ste //
NK005(ca)013:2794: h'u ni rab tu 'ching ba'i bdag /
NK005(ca)013:2795: b+h+yo ni rab tu bsdom par mdzad //
NK005(ca)013:2796: h'u gis skyod nas bde chen 'bebs //
NK005(ca)013:2797: 'bru brgyad sngags kyis sgrub par mdzod //
NK005(ca)013:2798: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK005(ca)013:2799: zhes mnyam par sbyor ba'i mkha' las byang sems mu tig dkar po lta bu las 'phros /
NK005(ca)013:2800: de nyid 'dod yon lnga'i lha mo mang por gyur
NK005(ca)013:2801: te dkyil 'khor pa la mchod pas mnyes par mos
NK005(ca)013:2803: spros med rtog bral mkha' dbyings dag pa nas //
NK005(ca)013:2804: skye med rdo rje'i sku gsung thugs mnga' ba //
NK005(ca)013:2805: 'gro mgon rang byung bcom ldan thugs rje'i lha //
NK005(ca)013:2806: zhi khro rab 'byams ma lus 'khor dang bcas //
NK005(ca)013:2807: stong nyid dbyings las thugs dam rgyud bskul gyis //
NK005(ca)013:2808: sprul pa'i dbyings nas rol cing gshegs nas kyang //
NK005(ca)013:2809: ye shes rtog bral byang sems mchod pa yis //
NK005(ca)013:2810: dgongs spyod zab mo'i thugs dam 'dis bskang la //
NK005(ca)013:2811: skye med chos sku'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK005(ca)013:2812: bo d+hi tsit+ta p+au dza a a /
NK005(ca)013:2813: zhes mchod pas thugs dam bskangs shing nyams chag sor chud /
NK005(ca)013:2814: byin rlabs thams cad gyi rnam par 'dus pa mtheb
NK005(ca)013:2815: srin gyis blangs te myang bas mtshan rtog thams cad
NK005(ca)013:2816: chos nyid kyi klong du grol bar mos te dngos
NK005(ca)013:2820: bsgral mchod ni ma tram bsgral chog gam bam chen
NK005(ca)013:2821: gyi mchod pa bya bar gsungs kyang sa bcad tsam
NK005(ca)013:2822: du / rtogs pas bdag grol gyi lta dgongs dang
NK005(ca)013:2823: ma bral bas thugs rjes gzhan sgrol gyi ting nge
NK005(ca)013:2825: rang gi thugs ka nas ram dpag tu med pa chad /
NK005(ca)013:2827: ram las ye shes kyi me 'bar bas sems can
NK005(ca)013:2828: thams cad kyi snying nang na gnas pa'i rigs drug
NK005(ca)013:2829: gi sa bon bag chags dang bcas pa bsregs /
NK005(ca)013:2830: rnam shes chos kyi dbyings su bsgral bar bsam zhing /
NK005(ca)013:2832: tho mar bdag nyid rtogs goms bsgral //
NK005(ca)013:2833: de nas gnyis med blo yis ni //
NK005(ca)013:2834: blo ngan 'jig rten snying re rje //
NK005(ca)013:2835: gnyis su med par bsgral bar bya //
NK005(ca)013:2837: skong bshags ni skong chen lnga dag gyur dang bcas pa bya dgos la /
NK005(ca)013:2838: tshogs ni las byang ltar ro //
NK005(ca)013:2839: de dag kyang thun so so'i mjug tu res mos byas na bde bar mngon no //
NK005(ca)013:2840: de nas dam rdzas kyi mchod pa dang 'brel bar gzhi bstod phrin bcol dang bcas pa bya ste /
NK005(ca)013:2841: gtor ma sman rag gis mchod cing dbyangs rol dang bcas pas /
NK005(ca)013:2843: mi gnas ye shes chos sku dag pa las //
NK005(ca)013:2844: rtogs pa 'bar ba'i ye shes phyag rgya ni //
NK005(ca)013:2845: shin tu mi bzad khro bo'i tshul ston cing //
NK005(ca)013:2846: gdug pa'i rgyan dang drag shul skur snang ba //
NK005(ca)013:2847: ya mtshan rmad byung khams gsum 'jigs rngams pa'i //
NK005(ca)013:2848: dug gsum rnam dag khams gsum zhal du shar //
NK005(ca)013:2849: thugs rje thabs kyi rgyu drug phyag drug rdzogs //
NK005(ca)013:2850: 'bar ba'i klong na mkha' 'gro'i sprin tshogs rnams //
NK005(ca)013:2851: gar dgu'i rgyan dang mi bzad cho 'phrul gyis //
NK005(ca)013:2852: bdud tshogs yud kyis 'dul mdzad rmad po che //
NK005(ca)013:2853: dug lnga ma spangs rnam grol lam du mdzad //
NK005(ca)013:2854: gzhan yang thabs tshul mtha' yas rgya mtsho yis //
NK005(ca)013:2855: ji ltar 'dul zhing sku gsung cir yang ston //
NK005(ca)013:2856: dus gsum rgyal ba'i yab mchog chen po ste //
NK005(ca)013:2857: thugs rje'i yon tan yid bzhin 'byung ba'i gter //
NK005(ca)013:2858: 'gro ba rnams kyi dpal la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK005(ca)013:2859: khro mo dbang phyug sku la nyer mdzad cing //
NK005(ca)013:2860: dus gsum rgyal ba kun bskyed thams cad yum //
NK005(ca)013:2861: 'khor ba mi spong mya ngan mi 'da' bas //
NK005(ca)013:2862: sgyu ma'i sku mnga' tshogs la mnga' brnyes pas //
NK005(ca)013:2863: rgyal ba rgya mtsho ma lus mkha' la bskul //
NK005(ca)013:2864: rdo rje dbyings kyi dam tshig bde mchog rab //
NK005(ca)013:2865: nam mkha'i spyod yul yid bzhin bsam rdzogs 'grub //
NK005(ca)013:2866: srid gsum mtha' dag dbyings dang mnyam par sbyor //
NK005(ca)013:2867: kro t+ai shwa r+ai phyag rgyas gsal 'bar ma //
NK005(ca)013:2868: 'bar ba'i sku mchog mnyes phyir sku la 'khril //
NK005(ca)013:2869: yum gyur dbyings phyug sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK005(ca)013:2870: bdag gis dus gsum sgrib pa kun spangs pa'i //
NK005(ca)013:2871: dug gsum ma spangs sku gsum lhun gyis grub //
NK005(ca)013:2872: yang dag grub mchog bdag la stsal du gsol //
NK005(ca)013:2873: nyid kyis zhal 'ches grub pa'i 'bras bu dang //
NK005(ca)013:2874: bdag cag las kyi 'bras bu mchis par mdzod //
NK005(ca)013:2875: bcom ldan khro rgyal khrag 'thung chen po yis //
NK005(ca)013:2876: sku gsung thugs las sprul pa'i mkha' 'gro rnams //
NK005(ca)013:2877: drag shul tshul gyis 'gro ba'i don mdzad cing //
NK005(ca)013:2878: gdug pa'i tshogs dang gnod sbyin cha lugs 'chang //
NK005(ca)013:2879: khro la khros pas zhi mdzad zhe sdang sku //
NK005(ca)013:2880: bdag rtog phung po 'joms pa'i ti ra phyar //
NK005(ca)013:2881: byams pa'i thugs kyis gnyis med don rtogs pas //
NK005(ca)013:2882: ye shes 'od stong 'bar ba'i ke r+ai ma //
NK005(ca)013:2883: zhi gnas rtse gcig gtod pa'i gzhu brdungs shing //
NK005(ca)013:2884: lhag mthong shes rab gcod pa'i mda' bkang nas //
NK005(ca)013:2885: nyon mongs bdud 'joms ye shes dbyings rum du //
NK005(ca)013:2886: dug gsum 'joms mdzad thugs rje tsoo r+ai ma //
NK005(ca)013:2887: 'dod pa'i rdul bral chags med pad+ma'i sku //
NK005(ca)013:2888: dga' byed dregs pa'i bdud 'joms rgyal ba'i rtags //
NK005(ca)013:2889: chos la dbang bsgyur chu srin rgyal mtshan phyar //
NK005(ca)013:2890: rnam rtog za byed khrag 'thung pra mo h+aa //
NK005(ca)013:2891: phrin las rnam bzhi cis 'dul btang snyoms sku //
NK005(ca)013:2892: thabs kyis khro bar mdzad cing gar stabs can //
NK005(ca)013:2893: 'chi bdag bdud 'joms ye shes rdo rje phyar //
NK005(ca)013:2894: shes rab dbyings la sbyor mdzad be t+aa li //
NK005(ca)013:2895: ye shes nyi mas ma rig mun bsal phyir //
NK005(ca)013:2896: nga rtog khrag mtsho 'khyil ba'i gting rum du //
NK005(ca)013:2897: thabs med rgyu drug 'khyams pa'i phung po lnga //
NK005(ca)013:2898: bde chen dbyings su 'dren byed puk+ka s+ai //
NK005(ca)013:2899: ye shes dbyings nyid ye nas gnyis med phyiir //
NK005(ca)013:2900: thabs kyi rdo rjes b+han dmar dkrug cing gsol //
NK005(ca)013:2901: sprin med mkha' la nyi zla'i gzugs brnyan bzhin //
NK005(ca)013:2902: ye shes 'od stong 'bar ba'i kasma r+ai //
NK005(ca)013:2903: 'jigs byed dur khrod tshogs rnams gzhom pa'i phyir //
NK005(ca)013:2904: thugs rje'i tshems kyis rnam rtog sgo 'byed cing //
NK005(ca)013:2905: drag shul tshul dang rngams pa'i stobs kyis su //
NK005(ca)013:2906: nyon mongs yid 'phrog za byed sma sha n+ai //
NK005(ca)013:2907: log 'dren bgegs kyi tshogs rnams bshigs pa'i phyir /
NK005(ca)013:2908: thabs kyis rag sha'i tshul du sgrol mdzad ma //
NK005(ca)013:2909: ye shes spu gri 'bar ba'i tshems brdar nas //
NK005(ca)013:2910: gdug byed lnga phung 'joms pa'i tsan+d+ha l+ai //
NK005(ca)013:2911: kun kyang ye shes 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NK005(ca)013:2912: dgongs spyod rgya mtsho dpag gis mi lang phyir //
NK005(ca)013:2913: sku mchog phyag mtshan cir yang ma nges te //
NK005(ca)013:2914: phrin las rgya mtshos ji ltar 'dul ba bzhin //
NK005(ca)013:2915: dur khrod 'bar ba'i gnas mchog dam pa 'dir //
NK005(ca)013:2916: bdud rtsi dmar gyi ar+g+ham rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK005(ca)013:2917: zhing chen gsar rnying tshogs kyi longs spyod dang //
NK005(ca)013:2918: byang chub sems dang m+aam sa rak+ta dang //
NK005(ca)013:2919: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba 'di bzhes la //
NK005(ca)013:2920: thugs rje'i dbang gis 'dir gshegs mchod pa bzhes //
NK005(ca)013:2921: bdag gis bcol ba'i las rnams 'grub par mdzod //
NK005(ca)013:2923: thun thams cad la mi nus na /
NK005(ca)013:2924: bdag med phyogs bral sogs res mos su brjod na'ang chog go //
NK005(ca)013:2925: gsum pa la bar gcod kyi bgegs mnan pa /
NK005(ca)013:2926: 'dul byed kyi gnyen po bskul ba /
NK005(ca)013:2927: dngos grub kyi byin chen 'bebs pa'o //
NK005(ca)013:2929: sgrub pa po rnams drag po'i chas su zhugs /
NK005(ca)013:2930: thog mar ye shes las dang /
NK005(ca)013:2931: rang bsten gyi pho nya gsum la phrin las bcol ba ni /
NK005(ca)013:2932: sman raka gtor ma bshams la /
NK005(ca)013:2933: ram yam kham dang 'bru gsum gyis byin gyis brlab /
NK005(ca)013:2935: rab 'jigs dur khrod 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NK005(ca)013:2936: dpal chen bka' yi srung ma thugs dam can //
NK005(ca)013:2937: ma chen ke r+ai brgyad dang phra men brgyad //
NK005(ca)013:2938: sgo skyong rnam bzhi dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad //
NK005(ca)013:2939: mkha' 'gro ging dang lang+ka 'bar ma dgu //
NK005(ca)013:2940: ma bdun sring gzhi pho nya rig pa 'dzin //
NK005(ca)013:2941: brten sgrub mchod nas chags pa'i rgyud srung sogs //
NK005(ca)013:2942: ye shes las las grub pa'i dam can rnams //
NK005(ca)013:2943: zhing chen g.yab mos 'dor gyis spyan ma rtul //
NK005(ca)013:2944: sman phud rak+ta sha rus zas kyis mchod //
NK005(ca)013:2945: dam bcas bzhin du thugs dam rgyud bskul na //
NK005(ca)013:2946: bar chad bgegs dpung 'dul ba'i phrin las mdzod //
NK005(ca)013:2947: ces bskul bas sbrul pa'i tshogs grangs med pa dang
NK005(ca)013:2948: bcas pas bdud bgegs 'gugs pa'i phrin las mdzad par
NK005(ca)013:2949: mos / nyu le'i ling+ga slob dpon nam las slob kyi mdun tu bkod la khebs bsal /
NK005(ca)013:2954: brub khung yangs shing gting zab pa'i nang du tri
NK005(ca)013:2955: las dngos grub la bar du gcod cing log par
NK005(ca)013:2956: 'dren pa'i 'byung po nyams len bdud kyi rigs su
NK005(ca)013:2957: gyur pa thams cad 'dus pa'i ngo bo rid cing
NK005(ca)013:2958: nyam thag pa'i lus can du gyur /
NK005(ca)013:2960: bden stobs gong bzhin brjod pa'i mthar /
NK005(ca)013:2961: dngos grub la bar du gcod cing log par 'dren
NK005(ca)013:2962: pa'i 'byung po nyams len bdud kyi rigs su gyur
NK005(ca)013:2963: pa thams cad mtshan ma rdzas kyi rten 'di la
NK005(ca)013:2965: tri yam dzahtri badz+ra am ku sha dzah dzahmh'u bam hoh lan gsum gyis 'gugs bstims byas la /
NK005(ca)013:2966: k+ai la'i sngags brjod bzhin byug bdug brab gsum gyis gzi byin bskyed pa'i phur bu /
NK005(ca)013:2967: stong pa'i ngang las h'u las byung ba'i sras mchog
NK005(ca)013:2968: yak+sha kro d+h+aa sku smad phur pa'i dbal can dus
NK005(ca)013:2969: kyi me ltar 'bar ba'i gzi byin can du gyur
NK005(ca)013:2971: e yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK005(ca)013:2972: 'bar ba gtum chen rngams pa la //
NK005(ca)013:2973: khros pa'i yid kyis mchod sbyin bya //
NK005(ca)013:2974: sangs rgyas bsod nams sku yang 'jig /
NK005(ca)013:2975: bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga la //
NK005(ca)013:2976: mtshan ma ming du bcas pa bya //
NK005(ca)013:2977: bkug nas rdo rje phur bus gdab //
NK005(ca)013:2978: rdul du byas nas brlag par bya //
NK005(ca)013:2979: ru lu'i sham bur sarba big+h+n+aana dush+t+aana m+aa ra ya h'u phata /
NK005(ca)013:2980: ces spyi gtsug ltag snying lte gsang kha mig ste gnas bdun du gdab /
NK005(ca)013:2981: rgya gram lhun po khro bo rnams kyis mnan par bsam la /
NK005(ca)013:2982: badz+ra su me ru trum h'u sa ma ya yash+tham /
NK005(ca)013:2984: dam sri mnan pa'i skabs su 'byung ba'i /
NK005(ca)013:2985: stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK005(ca)013:2986: byang phyogs stong gi sogs drag po'i bro tsam bya'o //
NK005(ca)013:2988: ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa kro d+h+ai
NK005(ca)013:2989: shwa r+ai sa ma ya de b+ai ta na shwa
NK005(ca)013:2990: d+ha ya ha na h'u phata /
NK005(ca)013:2991: bdag nyi dpal chen badz+ra he ru ka shin tu
NK005(ca)013:2992: 'jigs shing rngams pa'i skur gyur pa'i spyi bor gshin
NK005(ca)013:2993: rje gshed dkar po 'khor lo dang sdigs mdzub /
NK005(ca)013:2994: mgrin par rta mgrin dmar po sbrul zhags dang sdigs mdzub /
NK005(ca)013:2995: snying gar badz+ra he ru ka mthing ga rdor dril /
NK005(ca)013:2996: lte bar rdo rje gzhon nu ljang gu phur bu dang sdigs mdzub /
NK005(ca)013:2997: de thams cad kyi sku las rdo rje mtshon cha'i
NK005(ca)013:2998: char dang bskal pa'i me'i tsh+wa tsh+wa rnon po 'bar
NK005(ca)013:3000: sku'i gnas brgyad nas ha brgyad las khro mo go
NK005(ca)013:3001: r+ai ma brgyad zhal gsum phyag drug pa'i tshogs 'phros
NK005(ca)013:3002: pas bgegs thams cad bsregs bcom bskrad par bsam zhing
NK005(ca)013:3003: / rdo rje srin po'i ngur sgras /
NK005(ca)013:3004: badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+h+aa pad+ma kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai
NK005(ca)013:3005: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya ma h+aa yak+sha k+aa
NK005(ca)013:3006: la r+au pa karma ram ram dz+wa la ram h'u
NK005(ca)013:3007: phata / ces drag tu bzla zhing gu gul yungs thun rol mo'i sgra'i tsham rngams bya /
NK005(ca)013:3008: mdor bsdu na de tsam gyis kyang chog mod /
NK005(ca)013:3009: rgyud kyi dgongs pa ltar dus so so'i pho nya bskul bar 'dod na /
NK005(ca)013:3010: dus tshod dang bstun pa'i thun so so'i mjug tu
NK005(ca)013:3011: so so'i pho nya bskul ba'i 'dor len phyed par
NK005(ca)013:3013: dgong ka'i ting 'dzin mi gsal na //
NK005(ca)013:3014: sngon gyi dus nyul chen mo ni //
NK005(ca)013:3015: grib so sdud pa'i dbang mo che //
NK005(ca)013:3016: rdzu 'phrul bya rog skad sgyur ma //
NK005(ca)013:3017: de yi 'dul skal chen mo ni //
NK005(ca)013:3018: kha dog nub ka'i dmar thag 'dra //
NK005(ca)013:3019: ral pa ser sprin 'khrigs pa bzhin //
NK005(ca)013:3020: ral pa sprugs pa'i sgra gseb nas //
NK005(ca)013:3021: gza' rgod mig dmar char du 'bebs //
NK005(ca)013:3022: a la la yi phyag mtshan ni //
NK005(ca)013:3023: gnam lcags zhun ma'i khro chu bskol //
NK005(ca)013:3024: khros nas gnyen por rbad pa'i tshe //
NK005(ca)013:3025: khro chu khol ma'i skyin thang 'bebs //
NK005(ca)013:3026: srid pa'i gnam sa dkrugs pa skad //
NK005(ca)013:3027: srin po'i 'jig rten rba la g.yeng //
NK005(ca)013:3028: dam las 'das pa btso sreg byed //
NK005(ca)013:3029: khyod kyi phrin las skal phog pa //
NK005(ca)013:3030: dgong ka'i bar chad byed pa yi //
NK005(ca)013:3031: bdud byed thams cad thal bar rlog /
NK005(ca)013:3032: rak+sha ru dra yak+sha tshal pa ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK005(ca)013:3034: srod kyi ting 'dzin mi gsal na //
NK005(ca)013:3035: sngon gyi nyams len chen mo ni //
NK005(ca)013:3036: phyogs skyong bu mo ma rungs pa //
NK005(ca)013:3037: de yi 'dul skal chen mo ni //
NK005(ca)013:3038: thogs med rlung ltar rgyu ba mo //
NK005(ca)013:3039: srid pa'i rgyal mo srog gi bdag /
NK005(ca)013:3040: srid bdag chen mo kun gyi rje //
NK005(ca)013:3042: rtse gcig sgrub pa'i grogs mdzad ma //
NK005(ca)013:3043: khyod kyi phrin las skal phog pa //
NK005(ca)013:3044: srod la bar chad byed pa yi //
NK005(ca)013:3045: bdud byed thams cad rdul du rlog /
NK005(ca)013:3046: rak+sha ru dra yak+sha tshal ba ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK005(ca)013:3048: nam phyed bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK005(ca)013:3049: dkar mo phyogs kyi ma rungs pa //
NK005(ca)013:3050: de yi 'dul skal chen mo ni //
NK005(ca)013:3051: ral gri'i lus la rkang lag glog /
NK005(ca)013:3053: sngags pas gdungs shing bos pa'i tshe //
NK005(ca)013:3054: mchi ma thul thul char du 'bebs //
NK005(ca)013:3055: thul thul shig pa re res kyang //
NK005(ca)013:3056: dkar po'i bu bran mang po kun //
NK005(ca)013:3057: gzhob sgog rdog pas barjisa pa bzhin //
NK005(ca)013:3058: gso glags med par dmyal thag gcod //
NK005(ca)013:3059: rgyal ba'i ngag nyan dam tshig can //
NK005(ca)013:3060: khyod kyi phrin las skal phog pa //
NK005(ca)013:3061: nam phyed bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK005(ca)013:3062: thal ba bzhin du brlag par mdzod //
NK005(ca)013:3063: rak+sha ru tra yak+sha tshal pa ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK005(ca)013:3065: tho rangs bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK005(ca)013:3066: hor ston bu mo gdug pa can //
NK005(ca)013:3067: de yi 'dul skal chen mo ni //
NK005(ca)013:3068: mgo ni seng ge'i mgo bo la //
NK005(ca)013:3069: hur mo seng ge'i rang sgra sgrogs //
NK005(ca)013:3070: srin po'i gnam sa grum pa skad //
NK005(ca)013:3072: sngon gyi bskal pa dang po la //
NK005(ca)013:3073: rgyal ba'i bka' nyan dam tshig can //
NK005(ca)013:3074: khyod kyi phrin las skal phog pa //
NK005(ca)013:3075: tho rangs bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK005(ca)013:3076: bdud bgegs bar chad thal bar rlog /
NK005(ca)013:3077: rak+sha ru tra yak+sha tshal pa ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK005(ca)013:3079: shar ka'i ting 'dzin mi gsal na //
NK005(ca)013:3080: shar ka'i zer la bar gcod pa //
NK005(ca)013:3081: srab mda' ring la zhon pa mo //
NK005(ca)013:3082: de yi 'dul skal chen mo ni //
NK005(ca)013:3083: dung gi mgo la shel gyi lce //
NK005(ca)013:3085: gnam lcags thog gi ser chen 'bebs //
NK005(ca)013:3086: sngon gyi bskal pa dang po la //
NK005(ca)013:3087: rgyal ba'i bka' nyan tha tshig can //
