NK005(ca)013:3088: khyod kyi phrin las dus la bab //
NK005(ca)013:3089: shar ka'i rtse la bar gcod pa'i //
NK005(ca)013:3090: bdud bgegs thams cad thal bar rlog /
NK005(ca)013:3091: rak+sha ru tra yak+sha tshal ba ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK005(ca)013:3093: nyin phyed bar chad byed pa ni /
NK005(ca)013:3094: bying 'thib klub pa'i nad kyi bdag /
NK005(ca)013:3095: de yi 'dul skal chen mo ni //
NK005(ca)013:3096: sku ni dung gi 'khor lo la //
NK005(ca)013:3097: dkar nag gyon pa'i ya mtshan can //
NK005(ca)013:3098: srid pa'i gnam ni gos su gyon //
NK005(ca)013:3099: dregs pa'i sa ni gdan du bting //
NK005(ca)013:3100: khams gsum 'jig rten bang du khyer /
NK005(ca)013:3101: srid pa gsum ni khur du khur //
NK005(ca)013:3102: nyi ma'i skyin thang spyan nas 'char //
NK005(ca)013:3103: zla ba'i dmar mdangs zhal nas 'char //
NK005(ca)013:3104: lag na ri rab rtse dgu 'thor //
NK005(ca)013:3105: shin tu mi bzad gtum chen mo //
NK005(ca)013:3106: klu 'dul chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK005(ca)013:3107: 'di ni dpal gyi pho nya ste //
NK005(ca)013:3108: dus la bab po e ka ma //
NK005(ca)013:3110: las rdor gyi thun g.yas bskor g.yon bskor du brab bo //
NK005(ca)013:3112: gsang 'grel sogs las gsal bar ma gsungs kyang /
NK005(ca)013:3113: nyu le bskrad pa'i rjes thog der dngos grub sbyin
NK005(ca)013:3114: pa'i lha re'ang 'byung bas byin 'bebs pa'i phyag srol
NK005(ca)013:3115: ltar / zhwa gos spos rol gyis gzi byin bskyed
NK005(ca)013:3116: la gong du smos pa'i byin 'bebs dbyangs su bya
NK005(ca)013:3118: de lta bu'i las kyi rim pas sgrub pa'i zhag
NK005(ca)013:3119: du byed la nyin gsum mtshan gsum ste thun drug
NK005(ca)013:3120: gam / mi nus na gung gnyis bor ba'i thun bzhir sgo gsum g.yeng ba med par bya /
NK005(ca)013:3121: de la thun grangs gang byed kyang thun rjes ma
NK005(ca)013:3122: rnams la sgrub thabs kyi mchod pa byin rlabs nas
NK005(ca)013:3123: / gzhi bstod yan bskyar zhing nyu le sprod pa'ang
NK005(ca)013:3124: dus drug so sor byed na thun drug ka'i mjug
NK005(ca)013:3125: tu dgos kyang spros pas ngal na nyin mtshan lan
NK005(ca)013:3126: gnyis gnyis sbyor yang 'thus pas snga dgong gnyis kyi
NK005(ca)013:3127: / mjug tu bya'o // snga thun la 'dir bstan mthar chags su bya //
NK005(ca)013:3128: dzapa bzlas kyi skabs spyi srol ltar sgrub rten rnams dang sbrel ba'i gzungs thag slob dpon la phul /
NK005(ca)013:3129: nyin dang por thun dpon nas kyang gzungs thag blang
NK005(ca)013:3130: la de nas brtsams ru lu 'bru brgyad kyi sngags
NK005(ca)013:3131: rgyun ltar skad cig kyang ma chad pa dang gzungs
NK005(ca)013:3132: thag ras su ma bor bar bya dgos /
NK005(ca)013:3133: gung thun la sbyor sgrol mchod pa'i tshab tu skong chen dag gyur bcas btang /
NK005(ca)013:3134: de'i thog mar khrus bum logs su bcas pa la dmigs te /
NK005(ca)013:3145: zhes dam tshig khrus lung gi rigs pa ci 'grub
NK005(ca)013:3146: bzlas pa'i khrus chu des mar me'i skong ba'i rjes
NK005(ca)013:3147: su dpon slob kun nas khrus dang 'thor 'thung bya
NK005(ca)013:3148: / phyi thun la dngos grub bsdu ba'i rjes su gzhi bstod dang /
NK005(ca)013:3149: tshogs byin rlabs nas brtsams mchod bshags bsgral bstabs kyi bar du bya /
NK005(ca)013:3150: tshogs la rol ba'i skabs su 'jig rten pa'i cha gsum gtor ma btang /
NK005(ca)013:3151: mar gnas kyi lhag ma rnams sgrub pa grol nyin
NK005(ca)013:3152: bar phyir mi btang bar dkyil 'khor gyi lho nub
NK005(ca)013:3153: lcags snod lta bur bsags la khebs kyis bkab /
NK005(ca)013:3155: mchod pa byin rlabs nas mchod bstod nongs pa bshags /
NK005(ca)013:3157: bdag bskyed bsdu ldang gi bar du bya /
NK005(ca)013:3158: de nas ru lu chos nyid du shes pa la gsum /
NK005(ca)013:3159: chos nyid kyi go bgo ba ni /
NK005(ca)013:3160: cis kyang mi chod sogs dang ru lu brjod /
NK005(ca)013:3161: chos nyid kyi srung ba ni /
NK005(ca)013:3162: ming dang mtshan mar sogs dang sngags brjod /
NK005(ca)013:3163: chos nyid kyi lta ba la gnas pa ni /
NK005(ca)013:3164: phyag rgya'i cha lugs tha dad kyang //
NK005(ca)013:3165: dang por chos nyid ngang las byung //
NK005(ca)013:3166: bar du spyod pa ci spyod kyang //
NK005(ca)013:3167: kun bzang rol pa'i ngang du spyad //
NK005(ca)013:3168: tha mar rol pa'i snang ba yang //
NK005(ca)013:3169: chos nyid mnyam pa'i ngang du bsdu'o //
NK005(ca)013:3170: nam mkha' rdo rje sems dpa' che //
NK005(ca)013:3171: kun bzang yangs pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK005(ca)013:3172: rnam dag lam chen kun sgrol phyir //
NK005(ca)013:3173: mi skye mi 'gag cir mi dgongs //
NK005(ca)013:3174: zhes brjod la de'i don bskyang /
NK005(ca)013:3175: 'di gsum ni 'di tsam du ma zad thun mtshams
NK005(ca)013:3176: kun tu tshig brjod ma brjod gang ltar yang don
NK005(ca)013:3178: de nas bsngo smon shis pa brjod pas mtha' brgyan la /
NK005(ca)013:3179: legs ldan tshogs kyi bdag po gtso bor gyur pa'i
NK005(ca)013:3180: chos srung rnams kyi gtor chog rgyas bsdus gang 'grub
NK005(ca)013:3183: byin 'bebs pa gsum sngar ltar bya /
NK005(ca)013:3184: mtshan thun gsum po mchod brlabs nas brtsams 'dor len
NK005(ca)013:3185: sogs nyin thun ltar la srung ma'i gtor 'bul dang
NK005(ca)013:3187: thor thun mjug tu tshogs mchod bstabs pa'i bar du song nas bgegs mnan sogs bya'o //
NK005(ca)013:3188: sgrub pa'i skabs dmigs 'og tu ma chud pa'i 'grim 'grul dang btang len mi bya /
NK005(ca)013:3189: khyad par dam sel dang grib can gyi rdzas sogs rnam pa kun tu 'dzems /
NK005(ca)013:3192: phyir 'gro ba rnams la rdo rje rgyal po'am rgyal
NK005(ca)013:3193: thabs kyis srung ba bya bar gsungs kyang 'phral 'phral
NK005(ca)013:3194: mi lcogs na 'khyil ba'i sngags ring thung gis byin
NK005(ca)013:3195: gyis brlabs pa'i phur pa'am yungs thun 'bral med du
NK005(ca)013:3196: bcang / nang du 'ong thebs re la rgyal thebs
NK005(ca)013:3197: kyis 'khyil ba'i sngags kyis gsang gtor ram dud pa
NK005(ca)013:3198: bcang / sogs bya / langs pa'i tshe stan byin
NK005(ca)013:3199: gyis brlabs la phreng ba khro zhal du byas nas
NK005(ca)013:3200: srung ba sogs mdor na byung rgyal du mi spyod
NK005(ca)013:3201: par rtag tu dran shes bar ma chad pa'i rnal
NK005(ca)013:3203: dzapa dgongs bsnon lugs sogs skabs de dang der bshad pa ltar ro //
NK005(ca)013:3204: bdun pa dngos grub dbang gi phrin las la don drug tu gsungs kyang /
NK005(ca)013:3205: bar chad kyi bgegs bzlog pa da lta'i phyag bzhes ltar sgrub pa'i dkyus su sbyor zin /
NK005(ca)013:3206: bar chad dang dngos grub kyi mtshan ma brtags pa
NK005(ca)013:3207: ni deng sang dus kyi bsnyen sgrub tsam la yid
NK005(ca)013:3208: brtan 'cha' ba yin pas 'dir ma bris pa spro
NK005(ca)013:3209: na gzhung las shes par bya /
NK005(ca)013:3210: des na skabs su babs pa rang don du dngos grub len pa dang /
NK005(ca)013:3211: gzhan don du dbang bskur ba gnyis las /
NK005(ca)013:3216: nang mo dngos grub kyi cho ga bya ba'i de
NK005(ca)013:3217: ring dgong mo nas dkyil 'khor zhal bsgyur bar gsungs
NK005(ca)013:3218: kyang mi 'grub na mos pa tsam bya /
NK005(ca)013:3219: dbus kyi b+han+d+ha kha sbub tu bkod nas zhal mdun bstan du bslang /
NK005(ca)013:3220: ma mo brgyad kyi thod pa zhal phyir bstan /
NK005(ca)013:3221: dkyil 'khor gyi mdun ngos su gtsang zhing yid du
NK005(ca)013:3222: 'ong ba'i stegs la 'bru dkar gyis rdo rje rgya
NK005(ca)013:3224: sngar dkyil 'khor du bkod pa'i gsol byang gi sman
NK005(ca)013:3225: thod dngos grub kyi rdzas rnams dang bcas pa blangs
NK005(ca)013:3226: la bkod cing / g.yas su 'brang rgyas zla gam gsal shing dgus brgyan pa dang /
NK005(ca)013:3227: g.yon phyogs su rak+ta'i snod gzar bu dang bcas pa'ang bzhag /
NK005(ca)013:3228: gzhan yang zas sna bza' btung mang du 'du bya zhing /
NK005(ca)013:3229: de'ang mar thud sogs dkar ba'i rdzas shar /
NK005(ca)013:3230: shing tog khur ba sogs ser ba lho /
NK005(ca)013:3231: sha dang 'brang rgyas sogs dmar ba nub /
NK005(ca)013:3232: chang sogs sngo ljang rigs byang du 'god /
NK005(ca)013:3233: de rnams kyi steng du shing sgrom la brten pa'i
NK005(ca)013:3234: dar ram ras dkar la rdo rje rgya gram bris
NK005(ca)013:3235: pas bkab / sgrub pa po rnams rtags gsar du
NK005(ca)013:3236: gdab par gsungs pas lcogs na phyi thun dbu lta
NK005(ca)013:3237: pas bkab / bur bya / phyi thun la ru
NK005(ca)013:3238: lu dngos grub tu shes pa'i dzapa bzlas ci lcogs
NK005(ca)013:3239: pas bkab / bur bya / grub mthar / h'u /
NK005(ca)013:3240: bde chen dbyings nas khrag 'thung skur bzhengs te //
NK005(ca)013:3241: byams pa'i zhal bzang mngon du ston pa dang //
NK005(ca)013:3242: thugs rje'i spyan gyis rtag tu bdag la gzigs //
NK005(ca)013:3243: rtse gcig gdung ba'i rnal 'byor sgrub pa po //
NK005(ca)013:3244: kun la byin gyis rlob cing bzhugs pa dang //
NK005(ca)013:3245: dbang dang dngos grub dus 'di nyid du stsol //
NK005(ca)013:3246: bde chen dbyings nas ma brgyad skur bzhengs te //
NK005(ca)013:3247: byams pa'i zhal bzang sogs snga ma ltar sbyar bas snyan gsan dbab /
NK005(ca)013:3248: dngos grub rdzas kyi steng du rta mgrin dbang chen yab yum bzhugs pas srung bar mos /
NK005(ca)013:3249: grol ba'i nang mo snga bar phrin las bzlas pa gzhi bstod kyi bar dkyus ltar btang /
NK005(ca)013:3250: de nas tshogs bsgral bstabs cha gsum btang ba yan grub nas /
NK005(ca)013:3251: 'byung po lta nyan tshar gcod pa'i phyir /
NK005(ca)013:3253: rnal 'byor chen po'i sogs kyis mtshams bcad la srung 'khor bsgom /
NK005(ca)013:3254: lha dang 'khon gcugs sbyong ba'i phyir /
NK005(ca)013:3255: ye nas mnyam nyid kyis bshags /
NK005(ca)013:3257: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yi //
NK005(ca)013:3259: rang nyid gzi byin bskyed pa'i phyir /
NK005(ca)013:3260: nam mkha'i mtha' mnyam sogs kyis byin dbab /
NK005(ca)013:3261: sman raka gtor ma'i byin rlabs sgrub thabs ltar bya'o //
NK005(ca)013:3262: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la gsum /
NK005(ca)013:3265: khyad par sgrub rten las dngos grub blang ba'o //
NK005(ca)013:3269: dang po la'ang lnga'i thog mar ye shes lha'i dngos grub blang ba la /
NK005(ca)013:3270: h'u dang po gsum gyi dgongs pa ni /
NK005(ca)013:3272: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK005(ca)013:3273: khyad par chen po bsgrub pa rgyal ba'i bka'i //
NK005(ca)013:3274: snang srid snang ba chen por shar ba'i sku //
NK005(ca)013:3275: ye shes chen pos brgyan pa'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK005(ca)013:3276: dur khrod gnas ni dpal chen 'khor dang bcas //
NK005(ca)013:3277: khams gsum bsgral ba'i don phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:3279: ban+d+ha chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang du rak+ta ye
NK005(ca)013:3280: shes kyi 'od zer phyogs med du 'bar ba'i dbus
NK005(ca)013:3281: su dpal chen lha dgu'i ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor
NK005(ca)013:3282: skad cig gis gsal bar gyur /
NK005(ca)013:3284: brjod de rak+ta lan gcig sbrengs pas /
NK005(ca)013:3285: phyi snod 'jig rten zla gam dbang gi gzhal yas khang /
NK005(ca)013:3286: nang bcud kyi skye 'gro thams cad dngos grub kyi rdzas mchog tu gyur /
NK005(ca)013:3287: bde bar gshegs pa ma lus pa thams cad chos
NK005(ca)013:3288: nyid kyi ngang las phyag rgya ye shes kyi skur
NK005(ca)013:3290: mdun gyi nam mkha' la til gyi gong bu bzhin
NK005(ca)013:3291: du gtams te 'od phung 'bar 'dres su bzhugs par
NK005(ca)013:3292: gyur / byang chub sems dang m+aam sa rak+ta dang //
NK005(ca)013:3293: dri chen bdud rtsi'i chu dang rnam pa lnga //
NK005(ca)013:3294: rgyu gnyis rkyen gsum sbyar ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK005(ca)013:3295: rgya ba zhi khro'i tshogs la mchod pa 'bul //
NK005(ca)013:3299: rak+ta'i 'od zer phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa'i bye
NK005(ca)013:3300: brag dpag tu med par gyur nas mchod pas mnyes
NK005(ca)013:3302: mnyam pa nyid kyi pho brang rab 'byams na //
NK005(ca)013:3303: zhi khro ma lus rgyal ba yab yum tshogs //
NK005(ca)013:3304: khyod la ci mnga' yon tan bsam mi khyab //
NK005(ca)013:3305: dmigs kyis bskur zhing dngos grub stsol ba ni //
NK005(ca)013:3306: rnam par mi rtog ci yang sa ler mkhyen //
NK005(ca)013:3307: thams cad mkhyen pa'i dngos grub chen po dang //
NK005(ca)013:3308: spangs len med pa mnyam pa'i ngang nyid las //
NK005(ca)013:3309: lhun gyis grub pa'i dngos grub chen po dang //
NK005(ca)013:3310: skye shi med pa'i tshe yi dngos grub dang //
NK005(ca)013:3311: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub chen po rnams //
NK005(ca)013:3312: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i tshul gyis gsol 'debs na //
NK005(ca)013:3313: dus las mi 'da' rdo rje tha tshig can //
NK005(ca)013:3314: skyabs las mi g.yel yal gam gcig pa rnams //
NK005(ca)013:3315: thugs rje'i dbang gis dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK005(ca)013:3317: zhes brjod de rak+ta lan gsum sbrengs bas /
NK005(ca)013:3318: thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul te /
NK005(ca)013:3319: sgrub pa po rnams la dngos grub stsol ba'i dus
NK005(ca)013:3320: la babs pa'i sgra byung bas thugs dam gyi rgyud
NK005(ca)013:3321: bskul te dngos grub stsol cig pa'i nyer bsdogs su
NK005(ca)013:3322: gnas par gyur / h'u bar pa gsum gyi dgongs pa la gtso 'khor re re bzhin bstod pa /
NK005(ca)013:3326: dngos grub blang ba rnams bya bar gsungs kyang gtso
NK005(ca)013:3327: 'khor dgu po thun mong du bstod cing bsnyen pa
NK005(ca)013:3329: bder gshegs thams cad mnyam nyid thugs kyi ngang //
NK005(ca)013:3330: ma skyes rdo rje kun tu bzang po ni //
NK005(ca)013:3331: thabs la mkhas pas khro rgyal skur ston pa //
NK005(ca)013:3332: kun bzang he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK005(ca)013:3333: rnam dag dgyes chags dpal chen sku la sbyor //
NK005(ca)013:3334: yab yum gnyis med h'u gi dbyings nas gsal //
NK005(ca)013:3335: mkha' dbyings dkyil 'khor gsang ba'i yum chen ma //
NK005(ca)013:3336: yum chen dpal 'bar ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK005(ca)013:3337: thugs kar ljags steng h'u la 'bru brgyad bskor byas shing //
NK005(ca)013:3338: rnam gsum tshul gyis ma 'khrul bzlas brjod 'bul //
NK005(ca)013:3339: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)013:3340: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK005(ca)013:3341: zhes stong rtsa brgyad bzlas pa'i tshe /
NK005(ca)013:3342: bdag gi thugs ka nas ye shes kyi 'od zer
NK005(ca)013:3343: las mchod pa'i bye brag tu gyur pas ye shes
NK005(ca)013:3344: kyi lha la mchod pas mnyes par byas /
NK005(ca)013:3345: lha yi thugs ka nas ye shes kyi 'od zer tshul 'dus pas bdag gi sgrib pa sbyangs shing /
NK005(ca)013:3346: dngos grub kyi snod du rung bar byas pas mos /
NK005(ca)013:3348: rnam shes brgyad las khro mo'i skur snang ba //
NK005(ca)013:3349: phyag rgya cha lugs gcig tu ma nges kyang //
NK005(ca)013:3350: thugs rjes kun la khyab pa'i don mdzad ma //
NK005(ca)013:3351: ke'u r+ai khro mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK005(ca)013:3352: thugs kar b+hany+dzara ha la 'bru brgyad bskor //
NK005(ca)013:3353: rnam gsum tshul gyis ma 'khrul bzlas brjod 'bul //
NK005(ca)013:3354: spro bsdu sngar ltar byas la ma mo brgyad so
NK005(ca)013:3355: so'i sngags la ru lu btags pa brgya rtsa sogs
NK005(ca)013:3356: bzla / de nas mchod pa ni /
NK005(ca)013:3358: zhes rak+ta lan gcig sbrengs pas /
NK005(ca)013:3359: rak+ta las mchod pa'i sprin phung mtha' yas pa 'phros pas mnyes par mos la /
NK005(ca)013:3361: tshogs rje tshogs bdag dpal chen he ru ka /
NK005(ca)013:3362: 'bar ba'i rgyal po khrag 'thung chen po la //
NK005(ca)013:3363: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK005(ca)013:3364: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK005(ca)013:3365: dpal chen sku la gnyis med lhun sbyor ba //
NK005(ca)013:3366: kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai rigs kyi yum mchog la //
NK005(ca)013:3367: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK005(ca)013:3368: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK005(ca)013:3369: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)013:3370: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)013:3371: ma h+aa rak+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)013:3372: mthing ga mchod bsnams rdo rje gsang ba'i yum //
NK005(ca)013:3373: ke'u r+ai la sogs khro mo brgyad rnams la //
NK005(ca)013:3374: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK005(ca)013:3375: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK005(ca)013:3377: ma h+aa pany+tsa sogs btags pas mchod /
NK005(ca)013:3380: bde chen dbyings nas khrag 'thung yab yum dang //
NK005(ca)013:3381: ke'u r+ai ma mo brgyad sogs sku bzhengs shig /
NK005(ca)013:3382: dpal chen khrag 'thung thugs ni rin po che //
NK005(ca)013:3383: ru lu ru lu'i phreng bas rab bskor te //
NK005(ca)013:3384: lha dang gnyis su med par bdag sbyor bas //
NK005(ca)013:3385: rtse gcig sgrub pa rnal 'byor zab mo'i mthu //
NK005(ca)013:3386: deng 'dir nyid du bdag la 'bab gyur cig /
NK005(ca)013:3390: ye shes 'od zer gyi rtse las lcags kyu'i rdul phran mang po 'phros /
NK005(ca)013:3391: dpal chen lha dgu'i dngos grub thams cad bsdus nas rak+ta la thim /
NK005(ca)013:3392: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor yang 'od du zhu nas ltem mer gyur bar mos /
NK005(ca)013:3395: zhes rak+ta lan gcig sbrengs pas /
NK005(ca)013:3398: h'u mthing ga gsum du gsal bar mos la mtheb
NK005(ca)013:3399: srin sbyar bas rak+ta'i thig le gnas gsum du bkod
NK005(ca)013:3401: lce yi rdo rje dam tshig la //
NK005(ca)013:3402: rdo rje can gyis h'u bsgom ste //
NK005(ca)013:3403: bdud rtsi lnga yi sbyor ba yis //
NK005(ca)013:3404: zos na dngos grub gsum thob 'gyur //
NK005(ca)013:3406: w+aa ka sid+d+hi +aah tsit+ta sid+d+hi h'u /
NK005(ca)013:3407: 'bru gsum 'od zer dang bcas pa bdag gi gnas
NK005(ca)013:3408: gsum du thim pas bdag nyid dpal chen po 'khor
NK005(ca)013:3409: dang bcas pa'i sku gsung thugs ye shes phyag rgya'i
NK005(ca)013:3410: dkyil 'khor mngon du gyur par mos /
NK005(ca)013:3411: gnyis pa dzapa kyi grangs 'bul zhing rdzas byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK005(ca)013:3413: bde bar gshegs so khro rgyal gtso //
NK005(ca)013:3414: bzlas brjod mchod pa bla na med //
NK005(ca)013:3415: byin gyis brlab kyis byin rlobs shig /
NK005(ca)013:3416: bzlas brjod bsnyen pa bzhes su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:3417: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK005(ca)013:3418: hoh ye shes kyi bde bar gshegs pa //
NK005(ca)013:3419: dpal chen 'khor dang bcas pa la //
NK005(ca)013:3420: deng phan chad bsnyen pa dang /
NK005(ca)013:3423: sgrub pa chen po bgyis pa'i bzlas brjod kyi grangs
NK005(ca)013:3424: ci mchis pa thams cad thugs kyi gter du 'bul
NK005(ca)013:3427: de nas dngos grub bsdu ba ni sgrub pa po rnams bzhengs la /
NK005(ca)013:3428: +aahmh'u badz+ra a mri ta h'u h+r+aihth+aa /
NK005(ca)013:3429: zhes dgu pa'i dzapa dbyangs ci 'grub byas la /
NK005(ca)013:3430: dngos grub kyi rdzas thams cad bdud rtsi chen po'i
NK005(ca)013:3431: rang bzhin dang 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i rang bzhin
NK005(ca)013:3432: du byin gyis brlabs par gyur par mos la /
NK005(ca)013:3433: ru lu ru lu b+h+yo h'u //
NK005(ca)013:3434: zla gam dkyil 'khor rin chen dbang //
NK005(ca)013:3435: nub phyogs ngos su kha bltas te //
NK005(ca)013:3437: tshon gang yid bzhin rin po che //
NK005(ca)013:3439: ru lu ru lu'i gnas re che //
NK005(ca)013:3440: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK005(ca)013:3441: dbyangs drug blangs pas don drug 'grub //
NK005(ca)013:3442: sngags kyi yi ge sgra sgrogs pas //
NK005(ca)013:3443: des ni dkyil 'khor lha rnams bskyed //
NK005(ca)013:3444: zab ces 'brug ltar sgra sgrogs pas //
NK005(ca)013:3445: gtum po gdug pa lhan ner 'gyur //
NK005(ca)013:3446: khur pa dbugs kyi rlung 'byin pas //
NK005(ca)013:3447: khro bo khro mo'i sprul pa 'gyed //
NK005(ca)013:3448: rdo rje srin po'i dur sgra yis //
NK005(ca)013:3449: gdug pa thams cad spa yang bkod //
NK005(ca)013:3451: gnod byed ma lus rdul du rlog /
NK005(ca)013:3452: tshangs pa dbyangs kyi 'dren tshul gyis //
NK005(ca)013:3453: 'khor rnams thams cad dbang du sdud //
NK005(ca)013:3454: bdag nyid dpal chen skur bsgom ste //
NK005(ca)013:3455: thugs kar gsal ba'i 'bru brgyad po //
NK005(ca)013:3456: spro ni phyogs bcu'i nam mkhar spro //
NK005(ca)013:3457: sdud ni bde chen dbyings su sdud //
NK005(ca)013:3458: bsgrub ni dpal chen he ru bsgrub //
NK005(ca)013:3459: bsnyen ni dus gsum rgyal ba'i bsnyen //
NK005(ca)013:3460: bsten ni ma sring mkha' 'gro bsten //
NK005(ca)013:3461: mi gnas ye shes thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)013:3462: ye shes 'od zer slar 'dus ci li li //
NK005(ca)013:3463: 'phrul gyi zhags pa rnams kyang dbyings su bsdu //
NK005(ca)013:3464: gser gyi nyi ma rnams ni klong du byil //
NK005(ca)013:3465: h'u dang bcas pa'i ru lu'i phreng ba 'di //
NK005(ca)013:3466: thugs kyi gter du 'bul lo bzhes su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:3467: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK005(ca)013:3469: phyogs bcu nas sku dang ye shes bkrag dang gzi mdangs thams cad 'dus te /
NK005(ca)013:3470: dngos grub kyi rdzas la tham par mos /
NK005(ca)013:3471: gsum pa phreng ba 'bul ba ni /
NK005(ca)013:3472: me tog rigs kyi lha la 'bul ba'i mos pas /
NK005(ca)013:3473: byang chub rdo rjes sangs rgyas la //
NK005(ca)013:3474: mchod chen ji ltar mdzad pa ltar //
NK005(ca)013:3475: bdag kyang rab tu bsgral slad du //
NK005(ca)013:3476: nam mkha'i rdo rje bdag la stsol //
NK005(ca)013:3478: bzhi pa gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK005(ca)013:3479: hoh bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po sh+r+ai he ru ka yab yum 'khor dang bcas pa rnams la /
NK005(ca)013:3480: khyed la ci mang'i dngos grub rnams bdag cag rnal
NK005(ca)013:3481: 'byor sgrub pa po rnams la stsal ba'i mdo ni
NK005(ca)013:3484: thogs pa med pa'i shes rab /
NK005(ca)013:3489: khams gsum las rnam par rgyal ba'i dbang /
NK005(ca)013:3492: las rnam bzhi brtsams pa tsam gyis 'grub pa dang /
NK005(ca)013:3493: dbang bcu mthar phyin pa dang /
NK005(ca)013:3494: rgyal mtshan gyi dpung rgyan bzhin nub pa'i dus med pa dang /
NK005(ca)013:3495: rdo rje'i snying po bzhin du sra zhing mkhregs pa dang /
NK005(ca)013:3496: chu la mi bying ba dang /
NK005(ca)013:3497: nam mkha' las mi ltung ba dang /
NK005(ca)013:3498: brag la thogs pa med par 'gro ba dang /
NK005(ca)013:3499: rig 'dzin nam mkha' la 'gro ba la sogs te rig 'dzin byang chub kyi dngos grub rnams /
NK005(ca)013:3500: dus phyi so la mi bsdad cing las dang rnam par smin pa la bsnyad mi gdags par /
NK005(ca)013:3501: dus do nub nyid du thob par stsal du gsol lo //
NK005(ca)013:3502: lnga pa dza gad btung ba ni /
NK005(ca)013:3503: gsol byang bris pa'i bdud rtsi rdo rjes dkrugs la /
NK005(ca)013:3505: bkra shis mtshan ldan rdo rje ka p+aa lar //
NK005(ca)013:3506: dngos grub byin bsdus dpa' bo'i ro la phob //
NK005(ca)013:3507: ye shes rtsi bcud gnyis med bdud rtsi 'di //
NK005(ca)013:3508: skal ldan sgrub pa po la gnyis med bstim //
NK005(ca)013:3509: +aahmh'u sid+d+hi sid+d+hi a la la hoh zhes brjod la hub gsum gsum btung bar bya'o //
NK005(ca)013:3510: gnyis pa khyad par gsal shing gi cho ga la /
NK005(ca)013:3511: thog mar gang las dngos grub blang ba'i gzhi sgrub pa ni /
NK005(ca)013:3512: dkyil 'khor gyi mar me dgu po spar la /
NK005(ca)013:3513: dkyil 'khor dbus kyi mar me bcom ldan 'das badz+ra he ru ka yab yum /
NK005(ca)013:3514: phyogs mtshams kyi mar me brgyad goo r+ai ma mo
NK005(ca)013:3515: brgyad de khrag 'thung lha dgu'i phyag rgya bkra lam
NK005(ca)013:3517: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa sogs sngags tshan lngas dbang bskur /
NK005(ca)013:3518: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya sogs gsum gyis gnas byin brlab /
NK005(ca)013:3519: badz+ra sa m+aa dzahru lu ru lu h'u /
NK005(ca)013:3521: dza h'u bam hoh e h+ye hi ru lu ru
NK005(ca)013:3522: lu h'u b+h+yo dzahdzah zhes ye shes pa nam mkha'
NK005(ca)013:3524: dzahmh'u bam hoh badz+ra sa ma ya mu dra +aah
NK005(ca)013:3525: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka tish+tha sa ma ya lhan
NK005(ca)013:3526: / zhes pas pho brang gi mar me lhar gsal
NK005(ca)013:3527: ba la gnyis med du bstims nas brtan par bzhugs
NK005(ca)013:3528: / su gsol lo // de nas dngos grub blang ba'i las rim la /
NK005(ca)013:3529: spyan drangs mchod dang bzlas pa dang //
NK005(ca)013:3530: bstod dang smon lam bsdu ba drug /
NK005(ca)013:3531: ces don drug gi sgo nas blang bar bshad pas /
NK005(ca)013:3532: dang po gtso bo yab yum las blang ba ni /
NK005(ca)013:3533: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas te /
NK005(ca)013:3534: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK005(ca)013:3535: ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)013:3536: badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK005(ca)013:3537: zhes dkyil 'khor gyi mar me dbus ma las dpal
NK005(ca)013:3538: 'bar gyis me blangs te 'brang rgyas kyi gsal shing
NK005(ca)013:3540: pho brang dbus kyi dpal chen po badz+ra he ru
NK005(ca)013:3541: ka yab yum 'od dang sprul par bcas te gsal
NK005(ca)013:3542: shing gi rtse mor byon par gyur par mos la
NK005(ca)013:3543: / ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)013:3544: ma h+aa ba lim ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)013:3545: ma h+aa rak+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)013:3546: zhes sman gtor rak+tasa mchod nas /
NK005(ca)013:3548: bcom ldan 'das badz+ra he ru ka /
NK005(ca)013:3549: yum chen kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai ste //
NK005(ca)013:3550: gtso bo yab yum thugs ka nas //
NK005(ca)013:3551: zur brgyad dkyil nas 'bru brgyad shar //
NK005(ca)013:3553: phar 'phros dpal chen thugs dam bskang //
NK005(ca)013:3554: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos grub stsol //
NK005(ca)013:3555: ces bskul nas gtso bo'i sngags /
NK005(ca)013:3556: badz+ra ma h+aa sogs bzlas la /
NK005(ca)013:3558: rdo rje rigs mchog bdud 'dul gtso //
NK005(ca)013:3559: gdug pa 'dul ba'i thabs chen pos //
NK005(ca)013:3560: bdud rigs rdul du zlog mdzad pa //
NK005(ca)013:3561: dpal chen yab yum sku la bstod //
NK005(ca)013:3563: gsol byang gi smon lam ni /
NK005(ca)013:3564: hoh bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po badz+ra he ru
NK005(ca)013:3565: ka yab yum la dngos grub tu gsol ba'i mdo
NK005(ca)013:3566: ni / bdag cag gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir tshogs pa rnams la /
NK005(ca)013:3567: shes bya thams cad la thogs pa med pa'i shes rab /
NK005(ca)013:3573: bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po'i sku gsung thugs kyi
NK005(ca)013:3574: bla man chad nas dngos grub kyi skal ba dang
NK005(ca)013:3575: rigs brgyud gang lags pa thams cad phyi mar bsdad
NK005(ca)013:3576: mi 'tshal bar dus da lta nyid du thob par
NK005(ca)013:3579: badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah zhes lan gsum brjod las /
NK005(ca)013:3582: gsum pas sku 'od du zhu nas rang la thim
NK005(ca)013:3583: pas sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi gzi
NK005(ca)013:3584: byin dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)013:3585: de nas 'khor gyi ma mo brgyad las blang ba ni /
NK005(ca)013:3587: badz+ra goo r+ai sogs kyis mthar /
NK005(ca)013:3588: badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah ru lu sogs btags pa brjod la /
NK005(ca)013:3589: phyogs mtshams brgyad kyi mar me las blangs te gsal shing brgyad po sbar bas /
NK005(ca)013:3590: goo r+ai ma mo brgyad 'od dang sprul par bcas
NK005(ca)013:3591: te gsal shing gi rtse mor byon par gyur par
NK005(ca)013:3592: mos la / sman gtor rak+tasa mchod //
NK005(ca)013:3593: ma mo brgyad kyi thugs ka nas //
NK005(ca)013:3595: phar 'phros dpal chen thugs dam bskang //
NK005(ca)013:3596: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos grub stsol //
NK005(ca)013:3597: ma brgyad sngags la ru lu sbrel ba bzla /
NK005(ca)013:3599: goo r+ai la sogs khro mo chen mo brgyad //
NK005(ca)013:3600: gdugs pa thabs kyis 'dul ba'i drag shul can //
NK005(ca)013:3601: sku mdog phyag rgya sna tshogs cir yang ston //
NK005(ca)013:3602: ye shes khro mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK005(ca)013:3603: hoh khro mo chen mo brgyad la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni /
NK005(ca)013:3604: bdag cag gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor sogs nas /
NK005(ca)013:3605: bsdu ba gsum yan chad gong bzhin tu bya'o //
NK005(ca)013:3606: gnyis pa thun mong rdzas las dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK005(ca)013:3608: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)013:3609: bang rim dmar po dag la rten bcas shing //
NK005(ca)013:3610: zla gam dmar po dag la dbang nod na //
NK005(ca)013:3611: mar me dgu po dag las mdangs phyungs nas //
NK005(ca)013:3612: b+han+d+ha mtshan ldan rnams la tha tshig bgos //
NK005(ca)013:3613: lha dang gnyis su med par mnyam sbyar nas //
NK005(ca)013:3614: ru lu 'bru brgyad bar chad med par bzlas //
NK005(ca)013:3615: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa rdzogs par phul //
NK005(ca)013:3616: zhag grangs dam bcas bsnyen pa mthar phyin nas //
NK005(ca)013:3617: ye shes lha dang rig 'dzin dam can dang //
NK005(ca)013:3618: dngos grub stsal ba'i gnas dus deng nub btab //
NK005(ca)013:3619: ye shes lha dang rdo rje slob dpon gyis //
NK005(ca)013:3620: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub rab 'byams rnams //
NK005(ca)013:3621: sgrub mchog bdag cag rnams la stsal du gsol //
NK005(ca)013:3622: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK005(ca)013:3623: zhes dang gong gi sngags brjod la dngos grub kyi
NK005(ca)013:3624: rdzas rnams phyed du bgos pa'i phyed ka zur du
NK005(ca)013:3625: bzhag / phyed sgrub pa po rnams la 'gyed /
NK005(ca)013:3626: de'i rjes 'brel du tshogs rdzas rnams kyang 'gyed la de nyid du rol bar bya'o //
NK005(ca)013:3628: hoh bdag cag dpon slob mched dang lcam dral rnams
NK005(ca)013:3629: kyis rdo rje'i tshe gsol bas tshe dbang phun sum
NK005(ca)013:3630: tshogs pa'i skal pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK005(ca)013:3631: ma h+aa m+aam sa gsol bas rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen po thob par gyur cig /
NK005(ca)013:3632: dza gad dpa' bo gsol bas 'gro ba mang po dbang du 'du bar gyur cig /
NK005(ca)013:3633: zla rgyas gsol bas tshogs gnyis yongs su rdzogs par gyur cig /
NK005(ca)013:3634: gal phyis gsol bas bsam pa thams cad lhun gyis grub par gyur cig /
NK005(ca)013:3635: zla phrom gsol bas chos nyid zhi ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK005(ca)013:3636: 'jam des gsol bas byams snying rje byang chub kyi sems dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK005(ca)013:3637: zhal zas kha ba dang mngar ba dang skyur ba
NK005(ca)013:3638: sogs ro rnam pa sna tshogs gsol bas zhi khro
NK005(ca)013:3639: sprul pa'i tshogs la mnga' brnyes par gyur cig /
NK005(ca)013:3641: gsum pa khyad par sgrub rdzas las blang ba ni /
NK005(ca)013:3642: b+han+d+ha rnams gnas gsum du bskor zhing gtugs la //
NK005(ca)013:3643: khro la khros pas zhi mdzad pa //
NK005(ca)013:3644: thugs rje khro dpal rngams pa'i tshogs //
NK005(ca)013:3645: 'bar ba'i byin rlabs rmad po che //
NK005(ca)013:3646: de nyid du ni bdag la stsol //
NK005(ca)013:3647: hoh bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po sh+r+ai he ru ka yum badz+ra kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai /
NK005(ca)013:3648: ma mo chen mo brgyad 'khor dang bcas pa'i sku
NK005(ca)013:3649: gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thams cad bdag rdo rje
NK005(ca)013:3650: rgyal po la sogs pa sgrub pa'i rnal 'byor mched
NK005(ca)013:3651: lcam 'dus pa thams cad kyi thob par gyur cig
NK005(ca)013:3655: mar me dgu po snying gar bskor zhing gtugs la /
NK005(ca)013:3656: hoh deng phan chad bsnyen pa dang /
NK005(ca)013:3659: deng nub sgrub pa chen po bgyis pas /
NK005(ca)013:3660: bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po sh+r+ai he ru ka
NK005(ca)013:3661: yab yum ma mo chen mo brgyad 'khor dang bcas
NK005(ca)013:3662: pa'i thugs ye shes su snang ba'i dngos grub thams
NK005(ca)013:3663: cad bdag rdo rje rgyal po la sogs pa sgrub
NK005(ca)013:3664: pa'i rnal 'byor mched lcam 'dus pa thams cad kyis
NK005(ca)013:3667: de nas rdo rje dang dril bu gnas gsum du gtugs la /
NK005(ca)013:3668: hoh bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po sh+r+ai he ru ka yab yum /
NK005(ca)013:3669: ma mo chen mo brgyad 'khor dang bcas pa bsnyen cing bsgrubs pa'i don /
NK005(ca)013:3672: 'bras bu sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thams cad
NK005(ca)013:3673: bdag rdo rje'i rgyal po la sogs pa sgrub pa'i
NK005(ca)013:3674: rnal 'byor mched lcam 'dus pa thams cad kyis thob
NK005(ca)013:3675: par gyur cig / sngags gong ltar brjod do //
NK005(ca)013:3676: de nas shis pa brjod pas dngos grub brtan par bya ba ni /
NK005(ca)013:3677: sems can don phyir nan tan mchog bskyed de //
NK005(ca)013:3678: ye shes thugs rjes bdag la dgongs nas kyang //
NK005(ca)013:3679: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub dam pa rnams //
NK005(ca)013:3680: bdag la stsal zhing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:3681: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK005(ca)013:3682: zhes rten 'brel snying pos basngagasa pa'i me tog gi char dbab cing rol mo'i sgra yang bya'o //
NK005(ca)013:3683: de nas sgrub gtor dang dngos grub kyi rdzas lhag
NK005(ca)013:3684: gud du bcad pa de nyid cha gsum du bgos
NK005(ca)013:3687: tha ma gter bum du 'jog go //
NK005(ca)013:3688: gnyis pa dbang bskur ba ni /
NK005(ca)013:3689: skabs 'dir snod du rung ba rnams la sgrub pa'i
NK005(ca)013:3690: dbang chen sbyin pa yin kyang deng sang de'i rgyun
NK005(ca)013:3691: mi bzhugs la / don du gnyer ba yod na'ang bum dbang ngam /
NK005(ca)013:3692: gtor ma'i byin rlabs gzhan nas 'byung ba sogs kyis rjes su bzung bar bya'o //
NK005(ca)013:3693: dedaga gis dngos gzhi'i las rim rnams bstan zin to //
NK005(ca)013:3694: rtsa ba'i brgyad pa las kyi lhag ma'i phrin las la brgyad /
NK005(ca)013:3695: sbyin sreg gtor skyong gter sba dang //
NK005(ca)013:3696: dkyil 'khor bsdu zhing nongs pa bshags //
NK005(ca)013:3697: smon lam shis brjod bsngo ba'o //
NK005(ca)013:3698: de la dang po sbyin sreg rgyas par 'grub na
NK005(ca)013:3699: lo chen rin po ches mdzad pa'i rgyud lung sbyin
NK005(ca)013:3700: sreg ltar zhi rgyas dbang gsum mam zhi ba sngar
NK005(ca)013:3701: ltar song na 'dir dbang dang rgyas pa'i sbyin sreg
NK005(ca)013:3702: dag bya / mi lcog na gsang 'grel dkyus ltar
NK005(ca)013:3703: bsdus te bya ba la sngon 'gro thab dang rdzas
NK005(ca)013:3704: dag bya / bsags pa / dngos gzhi me lha dang ye shes lha mchod pa /
NK005(ca)013:3705: rjes kyi cho gas 'jug bsdu ba'o //
NK005(ca)013:3707: me thab zla gam dmar po kha khyer mu ran
NK005(ca)013:3708: rdo ra me ris bskor ba'i lte bar nyi gdan
NK005(ca)013:3709: la rdo rje h'u yig gis mtshan pa dang /
NK005(ca)013:3710: phyogs mtshams kyi pad 'dab brgyad du thig les mtshan pa bkod /
NK005(ca)013:3711: tsan+dana sogs shing dmar po zla gam du brtsigs /
NK005(ca)013:3712: slob dpon gyi g.yon phyogs su stegs bu la mchod rdzas chu gnyis nyer spyod /
NK005(ca)013:3713: las gtor zla gam dmar po pad 'dab lnga pa /
NK005(ca)013:3714: sgrub gtor bsil ba'i cha shas cha gnyis re dang /
NK005(ca)013:3716: dngos grub kyi rdzas cha dang po rnams bkod /
NK005(ca)013:3719: yam shig mar khu rnams bzhag /
NK005(ca)013:3721: dbal 'bar rlung g.yab sogs kyang 'du bya'o //
NK005(ca)013:3723: phyi mchod rnams sgrub thabs ltar byin gyis brlabs //
NK005(ca)013:3724: sman raka gnyis sngags tsam gyis byin rlabs gso //
NK005(ca)013:3725: las gtor dang bsreg rdzas rnams la las bum gyi chu 'thor zhing /
NK005(ca)013:3726: badz+ra yak+sha big+h+nan+ta kri ta h'u phata dang /
NK005(ca)013:3728: stong pa'i ngang las ma dang a las nyi zla'i
NK005(ca)013:3729: ga'u'i snod du rang gi thugs ka nas h'u spros
NK005(ca)013:3730: pa yongs su gyur pa las las gtor rin po
NK005(ca)013:3731: che'i mchod sdong 'od zer 'phro ba dang /
NK005(ca)013:3732: bsreg rdzas rnams rang bzhin gyis dag pa'i bdud rtsi
NK005(ca)013:3733: 'dod yon drug gi sprin phung mkha' khyab tu spro
NK005(ca)013:3734: bas las sgrub pa la thogs pa med pa'i nus
NK005(ca)013:3736: de nas me thab bsang sbyang /
NK005(ca)013:3737: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum las thab khung dmar po
NK005(ca)013:3738: zla gam mu ran kha khyer dang bcas pa 'od
NK005(ca)013:3739: zer mtha' yas pa 'phro bar gyur /
NK005(ca)013:3740: rang gi thugs ka nas ram yig thab nang du
NK005(ca)013:3741: spros pa las ye shes kyi me rab tu 'bar
NK005(ca)013:3742: bar bsam la / ag+na ye dz+wa la dz+wa la phata /
NK005(ca)013:3743: ces dkyil 'khor dbus kyi mar me las dpal 'bar gyis me blangs te sbar la /
NK005(ca)013:3744: slar rang gi thugs ka nas ram yig thab dbus su 'phros pa gun+d+hera gyur /
NK005(ca)013:3745: de las 'od zer spro bsdus don byas /
NK005(ca)013:3746: ag+na ye dz+wa la dz+wa la h'u phata /
NK005(ca)013:3747: yongs su gyur pa las zangs kyi ra skyes la
NK005(ca)013:3748: gnas pa'i me lha dmar po zhal bzhi khro 'dzum
NK005(ca)013:3749: chags pa drang srong gi cha byad can phyag bzhi'i
NK005(ca)013:3750: g.yas gnyis lcags kyu dang bgrang phreng g.yon gnyis dbyug
NK005(ca)013:3751: pa dang gun+d+he bsnams pa'i skur gyur /
NK005(ca)013:3752: rang gi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros pas shar
NK005(ca)013:3753: lho nas me lha 'khor bcas bzhengs par bsam la
NK005(ca)013:3755: ye shes spyan gyi spyod yul nas //
NK005(ca)013:3756: me lha drang srong 'khor dang bcas //
NK005(ca)013:3757: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK005(ca)013:3758: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs me lha'i gtso //
NK005(ca)013:3759: sems can don la dam tshig dgongs //
NK005(ca)013:3761: dzahmh'u bam hoh ag+ne dz+ny+aa na sat+wa e h+ye hi
NK005(ca)013:3762: b+ha ga wan ma h+aa k+aa ru ni ka dri
NK005(ca)013:3763: sh+ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)013:3766: gzi brjid 'bar ba me yi lha //
NK005(ca)013:3767: 'dod pa thams cad rab grub cing //
NK005(ca)013:3768: thugs rjes sems can don mdzad pa //
NK005(ca)013:3770: ag+ne ye sa ma ya tish+tha lhan /
NK005(ca)013:3771: zhes dbyer med par bstim zhing bzhugs su gsol /
NK005(ca)013:3773: pad+ma'i rigs las grub pa yi //
NK005(ca)013:3774: me lha'i rgyal po drang srong mchog /
NK005(ca)013:3775: phrin las kun gyi dbang po mdzad //
NK005(ca)013:3777: ag+na ye a la la hoh a ti pu hoh pra ti pu hoh zhes phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)013:3778: nyer spyod rim bzhin phul la /
NK005(ca)013:3780: me lha'i rgyal po drang srong mchog /
NK005(ca)013:3781: ra skyes chibs shing glog las mgyogs //
NK005(ca)013:3782: bsreg rdzas kun gyi phyag tshang mdzad //
NK005(ca)013:3783: tshim byed khyod la mchod pa 'bul //
NK005(ca)013:3787: nee lbi d+y+aa kha kha kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)013:3789: me lha zhal cung zad gdangs pas sreg blugs kyi bdud rtsi'i rgyun drangs nas gsol bar bsam la /
NK005(ca)013:3790: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgyas gzar bu gnyis bzung nas /
NK005(ca)013:3792: zhes mar khu blugs gzar bdun gyis dgang gzar bkang
NK005(ca)013:3793: ba kha sbyar te pus mo'i nang las mi 'da'
NK005(ca)013:3795: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam bi ma la ag+na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)013:3796: bdag cag rdo rje slob dpon dang sgrub pa po
NK005(ca)013:3797: mched lcam 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyi dam tshig
NK005(ca)013:3798: nyams chag cho ga lhag chad las dang nyon mongs
NK005(ca)013:3799: pa las gyur pa'i sdig sgrib ma lus pa sh+aan+tim
NK005(ca)013:3801: zhes lan gsum gyis dgang blugs phul /
NK005(ca)013:3802: de nas gtor ma dang sman raka dngos grub kyi rdzas rnams phul la /
NK005(ca)013:3804: me lha'i rgyal po drang srong mchog /
NK005(ca)013:3805: mnyam pa'i ngang las kun snang yang //
NK005(ca)013:3806: chos nyid ngang las ma g.yos pas //
NK005(ca)013:3807: ye shes sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK005(ca)013:3808: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK005(ca)013:3809: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i sbyin sreg 'di //
NK005(ca)013:3810: drang srong me lha'i zhal du mchod pa 'bul //
NK005(ca)013:3811: bdag la sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK005(ca)013:3812: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam sarba pany+tsa a mri ta rak+ta ba lim ta ag+na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)013:3814: bdag cag rdo rje sogs 'dod gsol gong ltar sbyar /
NK005(ca)013:3816: a pra ti ha ta badz+ra ya s+w+aa h+aas yam shing dang /
NK005(ca)013:3817: ag+na ye s+w+aa h+aas mar nag /
NK005(ca)013:3818: sarba p+aa pam da ha na badz+ra ya s+w+aa h+aas
NK005(ca)013:3819: til nag mang du 'bul zhing 'dod gsol byas la
NK005(ca)013:3821: me lha'i rgyal po drang srong mchog /
NK005(ca)013:3822: bdud bzhi 'joms pa'i phyag bzhi pa //
NK005(ca)013:3823: zhal bzhis las bzhi grub par byed //
NK005(ca)013:3824: las kun mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)013:3826: yungs dkar nag thab tu 'thor zhing /
NK005(ca)013:3828: rig pa'i rgyal po khyod kyis las thams cad byed pas /
NK005(ca)013:3829: bsreg rdzas lha yi zhal du 'bul ba dang /
NK005(ca)013:3830: me nyid ye shes kyi mer byin gyis brlabs nas
NK005(ca)013:3831: bdag cag dpon slob 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyi
NK005(ca)013:3832: phrin las thams cad 'grub par mdzad du gsol /
NK005(ca)013:3834: de nas 'das pa'i me lha mchod pa ni /
NK005(ca)013:3835: badz+ra dz+ny+aa na dz+wa la ram /
NK005(ca)013:3836: zhes pas me lha nyid thugs rje ye shes kyi
NK005(ca)013:3837: me 'bar ba'i rnam par gyur ba'i klong du b+h+r+aum
NK005(ca)013:3839: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra b+hany+dza dz+ny+aa na man+dala
NK005(ca)013:3840: b+h+r+aum zhes pas dur khrod chen po'i gzhal yas khang
NK005(ca)013:3841: nang ma zla gam dmar nag sgo gcig pa /
NK005(ca)013:3842: phyi bar khyams gru bzhi sgo bzhi rta babs dang
NK005(ca)013:3843: bcas pa'i dbus su lha so so rang rang gi
NK005(ca)013:3844: gdan ji lta ba bzhin grub par bsam la /
NK005(ca)013:3846: ye shes spyan gyi spyod yul nas //
NK005(ca)013:3848: sems can don slad dam tshig dgongs //
NK005(ca)013:3849: gnas 'dir ma lus gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:3850: dzahmh'u bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)013:3851: badz+ra a ra li hohhrim hrim /
NK005(ca)013:3852: zhes pas sgrub mchod kyi dkyil 'khor las lha tshogs
NK005(ca)013:3853: rnams las rdor gyi so so'i sngags dang bcas pas
NK005(ca)013:3854: man+dala me tog gis mtshon par spyan drangs te slob
NK005(ca)013:3855: dpon la phul ba las me tog thab tu dor
NK005(ca)013:3856: bzhin du / ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka sogs so so'i sngags rnams brjod pas /
NK005(ca)013:3857: lha tshogs rnams rang rang gi gdan la bzhugs pa ni /
NK005(ca)013:3858: dbus su bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po badz+ra he ru ka yab yum /
NK005(ca)013:3859: phyogs mtshams brgyad du goo r+ai la sogs pa'i ma
NK005(ca)013:3860: mo brgyad 'khor dang bcas pa 'od zer gyi phreng
NK005(ca)013:3861: ba mkha' khyab tu 'phro bas phrin las thams cad
NK005(ca)013:3864: ar+g+ham me tog bdug spos dang /
NK005(ca)013:3865: zhes sogs sh+lo ka gcig gi mthar /
NK005(ca)013:3866: rak+ta tsit+ta shwa d+ha ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)013:3867: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga sngon du 'gro bas /
NK005(ca)013:3869: girti h+r+aih'i bar gyis ar+g+ham dang rnam lnga rol mor bcas pas mchod /
NK005(ca)013:3870: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyi ljags rdo rje 'od
NK005(ca)013:3871: kyi sbu gu can gyis sreg blugs kyi bdud rtsi'i
NK005(ca)013:3872: rgyun drangs nas gsol bar bsam la /
NK005(ca)013:3873: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK005(ca)013:3874: zhes bdun gyis bkang ba'i dgang blugs kha sbyar ba
NK005(ca)013:3875: ru lu'i mthar sbel tshig sngar ltar sbyar bas lan
NK005(ca)013:3876: gsum phul / sgrub gtor sman raka dngos grub kyi rdzas rnams phul la /
NK005(ca)013:3877: bdag med phyogs bral sogs bstod pa sh+loka bzhi'i mthar //
NK005(ca)013:3878: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK005(ca)013:3879: dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i 'bar ba'i sbyin sreg 'di //
NK005(ca)013:3880: dpal chen lha dgu 'khor dang bcas la 'bul //
NK005(ca)013:3881: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob par mdzod //
NK005(ca)013:3882: sh+r+ai he ru ka sa pa ri w+aa ra ma h+aa ba lim ta kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)013:3883: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)013:3887: til rnams kyang ru lu'i mjug tu rdzas sngags sbyar
NK005(ca)013:3888: bas bargya'am nyer gcig sogs bcu tshan lta bu'i mtshams
NK005(ca)013:3889: ji ltar rigs par spel tshig sbyar bas 'bul zhing
NK005(ca)013:3890: / gzhan yang lha rang rang gi khyad par dam
NK005(ca)013:3891: rdzas dkyil 'khor la bkod yod na de dag las
NK005(ca)013:3896: bdag med phyogs bral sogs kyis bstod /
NK005(ca)013:3897: yungs dkar nag thab tu 'thor la /
NK005(ca)013:3898: spel tshig gis phrin las gsol /
NK005(ca)013:3900: gtang rag gi mchod bstod mdor bsdus dang /
NK005(ca)013:3902: sngar ltar me tog gis spyan drangs te /
NK005(ca)013:3903: dkyil 'khor pa'i lha tshogs rnams sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor la gshegs /
NK005(ca)013:3904: gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa rang la thim par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)013:3906: ag+na ye dz+wa la dz+wa la h'u phata /
NK005(ca)013:3907: ces blugs gzar gyi mar khus me gsos te /
NK005(ca)013:3908: 'jig rten pa'i me lha sngar bzhin gsal bar bsam la /
NK005(ca)013:3909: yam shing sogs rdzas lhag ma rnams bsregs /
NK005(ca)013:3911: me lha'i rgyal po sogs kyis bstod /
NK005(ca)013:3912: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam sarba pany+tsa a mri ta ba lim ta ag+ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)013:3913: zhes las gtor phul la 'dod don gsol /
NK005(ca)013:3915: badz+ra muhs me lha ye shes pa rang gnas su gshegs /
NK005(ca)013:3916: dam tshig pa 'bar ba'i rnam par bsam /
NK005(ca)013:3917: ma tram bsgral chog skabs ltar las bzhi ka'am zhi ba'i bro brdung la las kyi rjes bsdu'o //
NK005(ca)013:3918: gnyis pa mkha' 'gro'i gtor ma bskyang ba la gsum /
NK005(ca)013:3922: de'ang tshogs kyi lhag ma bsdus te /
NK005(ca)013:3924: phyag dar bcas snod du blug cing /
NK005(ca)013:3925: sgrub pa'i dus kyi lhag gtor ke'u tshang du bsags pa rnams dang lhan cig tu khyer la /
NK005(ca)013:3926: las mkhan gyis dkyil 'khor khang pa nas goms pa
NK005(ca)013:3927: bdun cu'i sar lhag ma'i dkyil 'khor gtor ma dang
NK005(ca)013:3928: bcas pa bshams la lhag ma'i cho ga rgyas par
NK005(ca)013:3929: bya zhing / bshal chus brtan ma bskyangs nas /
NK005(ca)013:3930: slar nang du 'ong ba'i tshe srung 'khor gsal btab
NK005(ca)013:3931: pa'i nang du rnal 'byor pa 'khor bcas kyi gnas
NK005(ca)013:3932: lus longs spyod thams cad tshud nas /
NK005(ca)013:3933: me'i ra ba'i 'od zer gyi rkyen ngan bar chad thams cad kyi srung ba chen por bsam /
NK005(ca)013:3934: sgo drung du dong gru gsum brus pa la sngar
NK005(ca)013:3935: dam sri bkug bstims byas pa'i ling+ga snod bcas bzhag
NK005(ca)013:3936: / slar yang bkug bstims phur gdab byas la 'byung
NK005(ca)013:3937: ba go ldog ri rab dang bcas pas mnan la
NK005(ca)013:3938: / / khro bo'i tshogs rnams kyis mi 'chor bar
NK005(ca)013:3939: gzir mnan mdzad pa'i steng du yi ge h'u mthing
NK005(ca)013:3940: nag las rgya gram ljang gu me lce'i phreng bas
NK005(ca)013:3941: bskor zhing lte bar su ser pos mtshan pa /
NK005(ca)013:3942: badz+ra su me ru trum h'u /
NK005(ca)013:3943: zhes brjod pas de nyid gser gyi ri rab gru bzhi dpag tshad bye bar khyab par gyur /
NK005(ca)013:3944: de'i steng du bcom ldan 'das don yod grub pa
NK005(ca)013:3945: 'khor dang bcas pas pho brang btab pas khro bo
NK005(ca)013:3946: rnams kyang shin tu gzir zhing mi g.yo bar bskul
NK005(ca)013:3947: pa'i mtha'i bar du mnan par bsam la las bzhi'i
NK005(ca)013:3950: dngos grub kyi rdzas dang sgrub gtor bcug pa'i gter bum sgrub khang gi phug gam /
NK005(ca)013:3951: dkyil 'khor khang pa'i 'og tu dong zla gam dmar
NK005(ca)013:3952: pos bsgyur ba sman raka gi chag chag btab pa'i
NK005(ca)013:3954: de nyid b+h+r+aum las rin po che'i gur khang longs
NK005(ca)013:3955: spyod zad mi shes pa'i gter du gyur par mos
NK005(ca)013:3957: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)013:3958: sku mchog byang chub sems su rab bzhugs pa //
NK005(ca)013:3959: snang srid thams cad mi rtag dus byung na //
NK005(ca)013:3960: zad med mi zad gter gyis mdun nas bsu //
NK005(ca)013:3961: skye shi med pa'i tshe dang 'phrad par shog /
NK005(ca)013:3962: dus gsum sku gsung thugs su gter sbas pas //
NK005(ca)013:3963: dug gsum rnam par dag pas sku gsum dang //
NK005(ca)013:3964: sku gsum 'gyur ba med pa thig le'i gter //
NK005(ca)013:3965: rdzogs pa chen po thig le bde chen klong //
NK005(ca)013:3966: thig le bde chen klong du gter sbas pas //
NK005(ca)013:3967: snang srid thams cad bde chen sa la bkod //
NK005(ca)013:3968: lam gyi nang na nye lam der rdzogs pa //
NK005(ca)013:3969: thabs kyi nang na ma nor dam pa'o //
NK005(ca)013:3970: zad med byang chub sems kyi gter sbas pas //
NK005(ca)013:3971: dus gsum sangs rgyas sems can gnyis med de //
NK005(ca)013:3972: mi zad gter gyi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK005(ca)013:3974: bzhi pa dkyil 'khor bsdu ba la /
NK005(ca)013:3980: mchod pa gsar du bshams la sgrub thabs ltar phyi mchod byin brlab /
NK005(ca)013:3981: sman raka gtor gsum sngags tsam gyis brlabs la /
NK005(ca)013:3984: hoh bdag cag rdo rje slob dpon mched dang lcam dral 'dir 'dus shing tshogs pa rnams kyis /
NK005(ca)013:3985: deng phan chad du bsnyen sgrub zab mo bgyis pa la tshul bzhin du rngo ma thogs te /
NK005(ca)013:3986: lta ba zab mo'i gting ma rtogs shing spyod pa zab mo dang du ma longs pa /
NK005(ca)013:3987: le lo dang gnyid dbang du gyur nas ting nge 'dzin ma gsal zhing bzlas pa grangs nyung ba /
NK005(ca)013:3988: rtsa ba dang yan lag gis bsdus pa'i dam tshig
NK005(ca)013:3989: nyams shing dngos grub kyi gegs su gyur pa thams
NK005(ca)013:3990: cad chos nyid kyi ngang du bzod par gsol lo
NK005(ca)013:3991: // zhes dang +aa li k+aa li yi ge brgya pa bzlas la dkyil 'khor lan gsum bskor ro //
NK005(ca)013:3993: ras bris yin na ye shes pa brtan bzhugs bya /
NK005(ca)013:3994: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor bsdu ldang sogs dkyus ltar bya /
NK005(ca)013:3996: be g+aa pra ma yam zhes dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo mdun gyi nam mkhar btegs la /
NK005(ca)013:3997: gtang rag gi mchod bstod dang bzod gsol sngar bzhin byas nas //
NK005(ca)013:3998: khyed kyis sems can don kun mdzad //
NK005(ca)013:4000: dz+ny+aa na man+dala badz+ra muhs ye shes pa gshegs /
NK005(ca)013:4001: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor gsal btab la /
NK005(ca)013:4003: ye shes thugs ka'i h'u las ni //
NK005(ca)013:4006: lha rnams so so'i snying po sgra //
NK005(ca)013:4007: h'u ha he phata sgra 'byin cing //
NK005(ca)013:4008: byang chub sems su gcig par thim //
NK005(ca)013:4010: zhes dgu brtsegs su brjod nas sgrub thabs ltar 'od gsal du bsdu /
NK005(ca)013:4011: thun mtshams gnyug ma'i lhar ldang /
NK005(ca)013:4012: go bgo lus srung byas la srung ma'i gtor chog kyang dkyus ltar du bya'o //
NK005(ca)013:4013: de nas phyi mtshams bkrol ba ni /
NK005(ca)013:4014: tho bzhi dang sgo byang gnyis kyi mdun mchod gtor bsham /
NK005(ca)013:4015: thog mar shar gyi tho rtsar phyin la /
NK005(ca)013:4017: gtor sngags lan gsum gyis gtor ma dang /
NK005(ca)013:4018: badz+ra ar+g+ham sogs kyis phyi mchod 'bul /
NK005(ca)013:4020: 'jig rten skyong ba'i dam tshig can //
NK005(ca)013:4022: phyi rol skyong ba'i rdzu 'phrul can //
NK005(ca)013:4023: 'khor dang bcas pa thams cad la //
NK005(ca)013:4024: dam rdzas gtor mchod rgya chen po //
NK005(ca)013:4025: sngar mdzad legs pa'i gtang rag dang //
NK005(ca)013:4026: phyin chad gnyer du bcol phyir 'bul //
NK005(ca)013:4027: phrin las ma lus grub par mdzod //
NK005(ca)013:4029: rang sngags la ya hi gats+tsha btags pas gshegs su gsol /
NK005(ca)013:4030: sku yod na gtso bo brtan bzhugs bya /
NK005(ca)013:4035: phyi sgo'i rtsar phyin la gtor ma byin brlab bya /
NK005(ca)013:4037: ma tram sras mchog tu gyur pa de nyid logs su phye nas mdun du bzhugs par gyur /
NK005(ca)013:4038: e h+ye hi +aa ral+li i dam badz+ra ba lim
NK005(ca)013:4039: ta pra t+aits+tsha dzahmh'u bam hoh sa ma ya hoh
NK005(ca)013:4040: zhes lan gsum gyis gtang rag 'bul /
NK005(ca)013:4042: 'og min du gshegs nas dpal he ru ka'i thugs kar thim par gyur /
NK005(ca)013:4044: badz+ra karma sogs kyi gshin rje la mchod pa dang gtor ma 'bul /
NK005(ca)013:4046: lha srin sde brgyad 'byung po kun //
NK005(ca)013:4047: zhes pa yan dkyus ltar la /
NK005(ca)013:4048: bdag gi sgrub pa ma thon bar //
NK005(ca)013:4049: bsrung ba'i phrin las mdzad pa la //
NK005(ca)013:4050: gtang rag mchod pas mnyes nas kyang //
NK005(ca)013:4051: dam tshig bya ra mdzad du gsol //
NK005(ca)013:4052: ces dang gshegs gsol snga mas 'gre /
NK005(ca)013:4053: nang sgor byin brlab mchod gtor 'bul ba nas /
NK005(ca)013:4054: phrin las thog ser bgegs la 'bebs //
NK005(ca)013:4056: dngos grub bar chad bsrung ba yi //
NK005(ca)013:4057: gtang rag phul bas dgyes bskyed nas //
NK005(ca)013:4058: slar yang phrin las mdzad du gsol //
NK005(ca)013:4061: slar yang h'u mdzad kyi phyag rgya dang sum+b+hasa phur
NK005(ca)013:4062: bu thams cad gdab rim las ldog phyogs su bton
NK005(ca)013:4063: la / ru ru spu ru dz+wa la tish+tha sid+d+hi
NK005(ca)013:4064: lo tsa ni sarba ar+tha s+aa d+ha ni s+w+aa h+aa
NK005(ca)013:4065: la / / zhes brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas pa'i 'o
NK005(ca)013:4066: mas phur bu dang bgegs kyi bzhugs brnyan yod na
NK005(ca)013:4067: la / / bkru / bgegs rnams kyi smas pa sos nas rang gnas su dengs par mos /
NK005(ca)013:4068: phur khung yang re kh+aa dkar pos dgab /
NK005(ca)013:4069: de nas gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor dang sgrub rdzas rnams bsdu ba ni /
NK005(ca)013:4071: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)013:4072: 'phrul zhal yid bzhin b+han+d+ha'i rdzas mchog dang //
NK005(ca)013:4073: khams gsum bsgral ba'i dam rdzas sha chen dang //
NK005(ca)013:4074: ma rig mun sel mar me dgu pa gsum //
NK005(ca)013:4075: 'di la brten te lha dang dngos grub bsgrubs //
NK005(ca)013:4076: mchod pa ci 'byor phul nas sgrub pa bskyangs //
NK005(ca)013:4077: 'khor ba ngan song rnams kyang bsgral lags na //
NK005(ca)013:4078: dus gsum rgyal ba rnams kyang mchod lags na //
NK005(ca)013:4079: ma sring rgya mtsho rnams kyang bsten lags na //
NK005(ca)013:4080: mi gnas ye shes thugs kyang bsgrubs lags na //
NK005(ca)013:4081: dngos grub dbyig mchog rnams kyang blangs lags kyis //
NK005(ca)013:4082: dngos grub mchog thob dkyil 'khor gnas 'di nas //
NK005(ca)013:4083: ye shes lha dang srung ma 'khor dang bcas //
NK005(ca)013:4084: dang po'i gnas mchog chos kyi dbyings su gshegs //
NK005(ca)013:4085: nam zhig bdag gis dam bcas bsgrub pa la //
NK005(ca)013:4086: khyed kyi thugs dam mchog kyang de la gas na //
NK005(ca)013:4087: myur bar slar gshegs par yang dgongs su gsol //
NK005(ca)013:4089: chos thams cad skye med du mos pas a k+aa ro bzla zhing dril bu 'khrol /
NK005(ca)013:4090: g.yas rdo rje dang bcas pas lha mtshan rnams blangs la cung zad mgo bor bkod /
NK005(ca)013:4091: lhag ma rnams shar kyi tshangs thig nas dbus kyi
NK005(ca)013:4092: bar phyags la bum par blugs te bkur sti chen
NK005(ca)013:4094: bum pa de chus bkang ste slar 'ongs nas dkyil 'khor khang pa sogs la bsang gtor bya ste /
NK005(ca)013:4095: de'i tshul ni gsang ba spyi chog ltar ro //
NK005(ca)013:4096: lnga pa nongs bshags bya ba ni /
NK005(ca)013:4097: rgyas par na rdo rje slob dpon la nongs bshags dang gtang rag 'bul /
NK005(ca)013:4098: mched lcam gcig gis gcig la bzod par gsol /
NK005(ca)013:4099: dkyil 'khor ye shes pa la bshags shing smon lam du bya bar gsungs kyang /
NK005(ca)013:4100: bsdu na thams cad kyis slob dpon la phyag bya zhing skyems drangs /
NK005(ca)013:4101: sgrub pa po rnams gcig gis gcig la phyag byas te /
NK005(ca)013:4103: rje btsun bla ma rnams kyi spyan lam du //
NK005(ca)013:4104: sogs tshar gcig brjod pa'i mthar /
NK005(ca)013:4105: ye shes pa'i dkyil 'khor mdun mkhar dmigs la /
NK005(ca)013:4106: pad+ma r+aa ga nir ma la /
NK005(ca)013:4107: ka ma la mug ta ni /
NK005(ca)013:4110: cho ga la chags na chags pa ste /
NK005(ca)013:4111: yum la chags pa chags pa'i mchog /
NK005(ca)013:4112: khro bo'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)013:4113: phyag ni phyag rgya chen po ste //
NK005(ca)013:4114: snga dam gnyan po nyams pa mthol zhing bshags //
NK005(ca)013:4115: phyi dam gnyan po nod cing sdom //
NK005(ca)013:4116: bdag cag g.yar dam bskang gyur cig /
NK005(ca)013:4117: hoh las thams cad dbang du gyur cig /
NK005(ca)013:4118: dbang dngos grub tu gyur cig /
NK005(ca)013:4119: de ltar 'gyur pa dang gyur pa'i byin gyi rlabs kyis /
NK005(ca)013:4120: 'o skol rdo rje slob dpon dang /
NK005(ca)013:4121: mched lcam dral rnams kyi lus sems kyi rgyud la
NK005(ca)013:4122: las dang nyon mongs pa'i bag chags thams cad ston
NK005(ca)013:4123: ka'i ba mo la dpyid kyi nyi mas bzhu ba
NK005(ca)013:4124: bzhin du byang zhing dag par gyur cig /
NK005(ca)013:4125: tshe dang dbang thang dpal dang gzi mdangs thams cad
NK005(ca)013:4126: rin po che'i dpung rgyan ltar dar zhing rgyas par
NK005(ca)013:4127: gyur cig / rdo rje slob dpon yang ston pa'i
NK005(ca)013:4128: sgron ma yun ring zhing 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa
NK005(ca)013:4129: la mthu che zhing thabs mkhas par gyur cig /
NK005(ca)013:4130: chos chen po 'di yang rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mo ltar nub pa med par gyur cig /
NK005(ca)013:4131: yul phyogs 'dir yang dus kyi 'khrugs pa zhi /
NK005(ca)013:4133: mi nad dang phyugs nad rgyun chod /
NK005(ca)013:4136: bde skyid phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK005(ca)013:4138: drug pa smon lam la gnyis te /
NK005(ca)013:4139: yang gtso bor gyur pa ni rdo rje rgyal po'i bdud rtsi'i b+han+d+ha thogs te spyan drangs la /
NK005(ca)013:4141: mi gnas ye shes thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)013:4142: 'gyur ba med par lhun gyis grub pa dang //
NK005(ca)013:4143: rab 'byams rgyal ba'i bka' la dbang thob nas //
NK005(ca)013:4144: 'gro ba yongs kyi dpal du gyur par shog /
NK005(ca)013:4145: de lta bu yi man ngag lung ston pa'i //
NK005(ca)013:4146: bka' drin chen po dge ba'i bshes gnyen dang //
NK005(ca)013:4147: dam tshig srog gi bsdus pa'i mched lcam rnams //
NK005(ca)013:4148: 'og min lhun gyis grub pa'i gzhal yas su //
NK005(ca)013:4149: dus gsum 'du 'bral med par 'grogs pa dang //
NK005(ca)013:4150: gsang ba chen po thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)013:4151: bla med sku gsung thugs su 'grub par shog /
NK005(ca)013:4153: yum gtso bor gyur pa ni /
NK005(ca)013:4154: rdo rje gzungs mas mar me thogs te smon lam
NK005(ca)013:4155: bya bar gsungs kyang da lta'i phyag len dkyus bzhin
NK005(ca)013:4156: gzungs mar btags pa'am rdo rjee rgyal thebs kyis rjes
NK005(ca)013:4157: su dbyangs bor len bya zhing /
NK005(ca)013:4158: thams cad lag pa lu gu rgyud du sbrel bas mar me thogs la /
NK005(ca)013:4160: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK005(ca)013:4161: rdo rje slob dpon gnyan gyi dbu bzung nas //
NK005(ca)013:4162: rgyal ba'i gdung 'tshob mched dang lcam dral rnams //
NK005(ca)013:4163: nam zhig byang chub lam du bzhugs pa'i tshe //
NK005(ca)013:4164: 'khor ba'i g.yang sa chen por mi ltung zhing //
NK005(ca)013:4165: dmyal ba'i zangs khar rbab tu mi 'chor la //
NK005(ca)013:4166: gcong rong zab mo'i gnas su mi skye zhing //
NK005(ca)013:4167: mngal gyi srin bu dag tu ma skyes shig /
NK005(ca)013:4168: gcan gzan gdug pa'i sgra skad mi thos shing //
NK005(ca)013:4169: mtshon rnon gdug pa'i dbal gyis mi phog la //
NK005(ca)013:4170: 'khor ba'i mun nag chen por mi btang shog /
NK005(ca)013:4171: dge ba'i bshes gnyen bka' drin byams pa'i mgon //
NK005(ca)013:4172: mi 'bral srog gis 'brel ba'i mched lcam rnams //
NK005(ca)013:4173: tshe rabs 'di nas tshe brgyud gar skyes kyang //
NK005(ca)013:4174: mi 'bral rtse gcig 'grogs pa'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK005(ca)013:4175: sa bcu'i khyad par rim gyis bgrod gyur nas //
NK005(ca)013:4176: nam zhig 'chi 'pho'i dus tshe byung ba na //
NK005(ca)013:4177: 'khor ba'i g.yang sa chen por ltung srid pas //
NK005(ca)013:4178: snang ba'i go 'byed gsal ba'i zhun mar 'dis //
NK005(ca)013:4179: sgrub mchog bdag cag rnams kyi shul mtshon nas //
NK005(ca)013:4180: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i tshogs kyis mdun nas bsu //
NK005(ca)013:4181: yi dam rgyal ba'i lhas ni srog brten nas //
NK005(ca)013:4182: ma sring rgya mtsho'i tshogs kyis shul nas skyel //
NK005(ca)013:4183: byang chub sems dpa' brgyad kyis mtha' brten te //
NK005(ca)013:4184: byang chub sems ma rnams ni rol mo 'bul //
NK005(ca)013:4185: lcang lo can gyi gnas su phyin pa'i tshe //
NK005(ca)013:4186: rdo rje khro rgyal rnams kyi zhal mthong nas //
NK005(ca)013:4187: rig pa'i rgyal po'i zhabs drung skye nas kyang //
NK005(ca)013:4188: bla med sku gsung thugs su 'grub par shog /
NK005(ca)013:4190: bdun pa shis brjod bya ba ni /
NK005(ca)013:4191: thams cad nas zhwa gos gzi mdangs bskyed //
NK005(ca)013:4192: phye mar me tog thogs la /
NK005(ca)013:4193: rten snying dang zhal nas gsungs pa'i mchog gsum gyi shes pa brjod pas byang drangs la /
NK005(ca)013:4195: byang chub sems mchog shes rab ting 'dzin gyis //
NK005(ca)013:4196: nyon mongs bdag 'dzin rnam rtog kun spangs nas //
NK005(ca)013:4197: bdag nyid chen po'i don la rab bsgom pas /
NK005(ca)013:4198: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK005(ca)013:4199: rdor sems sprul pa skar ltar 'phro ba yi //
NK005(ca)013:4200: za byed bdud 'dul log rtog kun btul nas //
NK005(ca)013:4201: bla med byang chub mchog la bkod pa yi //
NK005(ca)013:4202: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK005(ca)013:4203: zhi rgyas dbang dang mngon spyod phrin las kyis //
NK005(ca)013:4204: rgyu drug sems can ma lus kun bsgral te //
NK005(ca)013:4205: bla med byang chub mchog la bkod pa yi //
NK005(ca)013:4206: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK005(ca)013:4207: bka' gsung sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor chen po ru //
NK005(ca)013:4208: rdo rje slob dpon mched dang lcam dral gyi //
NK005(ca)013:4209: thugs dam chen po yongs su bskangs pa yis //
NK005(ca)013:4210: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK005(ca)013:4212: gzhan yang shis brjod kyi tshig phreng rgyas par spel pas dge legs su bya'o //
NK005(ca)013:4213: de'i rjes 'brel du ma sring rgya mtsho mnyes par
NK005(ca)013:4214: byas pa'i slad du ru lu gar gyi bro brdung
NK005(ca)013:4215: zhing glu blang ba sogs kyang bshad do //
NK005(ca)013:4216: brgyad pa bsngo ba bya ba ni /
NK005(ca)013:4217: bla ma yi dam lha tshogs sogs spyi ltar brjod /
NK005(ca)013:4218: slob dpon gyis dgongs gsol sngon du 'gro bas bstan
NK005(ca)013:4219: pa spyi bsngo mdzad cing sgrub pa po rnams kyis
NK005(ca)013:4220: mthun 'gyur brjod / 'khor gsum rnam par mi rtogs pa'i rgyas gdab par bya'o //
NK005(ca)013:4222: sgrub pa po rnams zhag gcig phyi rol du mi 'gro /
NK005(ca)013:4223: de nas kyang zhag gsum la sogs par thag ring
NK005(ca)013:4224: du mi 'gro bar las gzhung tshar re bsrang zhing
NK005(ca)013:4225: dga' ston ci ltar 'byor ba bya /
NK005(ca)013:4226: bla ma ma yin pa la phyag mi bya //
NK005(ca)013:4227: de nas dal bus mtshams khad kyis grol zhing zhi
NK005(ca)013:4228: khro rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin dang ma bral bar
NK005(ca)013:4229: sgrub pa'i rjes don yod par spyad do //
NK005(ca)013:4230: de dag la gnad du che ba'i zhal gdams gsang 'grel las /
NK005(ca)013:4231: de la sgrub pa'i rnal 'byor du bya ba gang snyam pa la /
NK005(ca)013:4232: sgom rgyud gsal ba ci nus bya //
NK005(ca)013:4234: dang por mtshams bcad pa dang /
NK005(ca)013:4235: bar du zhi khro gzhung bsrang ba dang /
NK005(ca)013:4236: tha mar bzlas brjod dang mkha' 'gro ma bskyang zhing mchod pa yan chad du /
NK005(ca)013:4237: rab mtshan med mtshan bcas kyi bsgom par rang gi
NK005(ca)013:4238: shes pa'i rgyud la gsal zhing 'dris par bsgom pa
NK005(ca)013:4239: dang / 'bring sngags dang bzlas brjod bar ma chad par bya ba dang /
NK005(ca)013:4240: tha mar lung tshig gis gsal gdab cing bskul ba ste /
NK005(ca)013:4241: rnal 'byor pa'i sgo gsum g.yo sgyu med pas ci nus su 'bad de bya'o //
NK005(ca)013:4242: rnal 'byor pa rgod bag g.yeng ba can gyis ni ma yin no //
NK005(ca)013:4243: zhes gsungs pa'i don sgrub pa po'i nyams tshod dang
NK005(ca)013:4244: sbyar te rgyud la 'byor nges par bya ba cis
NK005(ca)013:4245: kyang gal che'o // spyi don gsum pa bsgrubs pas grub pa'i 'bras bu ni /
NK005(ca)013:4246: de ltar mtshan bcas mtshan med zung du 'brel ba mnyam bzhag gi rnal 'byor dang /
NK005(ca)013:4247: ting nge 'dzin gyi stobs kyis cir snang lam du
NK005(ca)013:4248: khyer ba rjes thob kyi rnal 'byor dang mi 'bral
NK005(ca)013:4250: rnal 'byor gsum gyi dgongs pa yi //
NK005(ca)013:4251: bsnyen sgrub rnam gsum rim par sbyar //
NK005(ca)013:4255: mtshan ma thob pa'i rnal 'byor rnam pa gsum gyi blo'i stobs dang sbyar ba'i /
NK005(ca)013:4258: gnam stong la zhugs nas nyal gdon pa dus kyi bsnyen sgrub rnam pa gsum mthar phyin cing /
NK005(ca)013:4259: so so'i skabs kyi nye rgyu dang bcas pa la /
NK005(ca)013:4260: gnas skabs lam gyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin bzhi dang
NK005(ca)013:4261: las bzhi grub pa chen po brgyad bde blag tu
NK005(ca)013:4262: 'grub / mthar thug dbang bzhi'i lam las 'gros bzhi thim zhing grub mtha' bzhi snyogs te /
NK005(ca)013:4263: de'ang rtsa'i 'gros kun dar mar thim pas sprul sku /
NK005(ca)013:4264: yi ge'i 'gros a ham zung 'jug tu thim pas longs sku /
NK005(ca)013:4265: lus khams bdud rtsi'i 'gros mi shigs pa'i thig ler thim pas chos sku /
NK005(ca)013:4266: snying po rlung gi 'gros bde ba chen por thim
NK005(ca)013:4267: pas ngo bo nyid sku ste sku bzhi dbyer mi
NK005(ca)013:4268: phyed pa rigs kun khyab bdag rdo rje sems dpa'
NK005(ca)013:4269: dpal he ru ka yang dag grub pa gcig pu
NK005(ca)013:4270: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde mchog gi go 'phang mngon
NK005(ca)013:4271: du gyur nas sangs rgyas kyi phrin las 'khor ba
NK005(ca)013:4272: ma stong gi bar du rgyun mi 'chad par 'byung
NK005(ca)013:4273: bar 'gyur ro // 'di ni gzhan 'grigs dang bya sla gtsor bton gyis gzhung don gsar bsdu dang /
NK005(ca)013:4274: rgyud dang man ngag gi don thun mong ma yin
NK005(ca)013:4275: pa gang yang med pa la gzhan spros rgyas 'gebs
NK005(ca)013:4276: kyi sgo nas dbang po che'i ras chod sogs kyi
NK005(ca)013:4278: gtso bor rgyud gal po dang /
NK005(ca)013:4279: pad+ma'i gsang 'grel chen mo'i dgongs pa drang thad du bkod /
NK005(ca)013:4280: gter chen chos kyi rgyal po'i gsung rab lha dgu'i
NK005(ca)013:4281: sgrub dkyil la sbyor ba'i dbang du byas shing zla
NK005(ca)013:4283: zhi khro gnas bsgyur gyi dkyil 'khor zla gam lnga bcu rtsa brgyad pa dang /
NK005(ca)013:4284: drug cu rtsa brgyad pa rnams la'ang kha spo chog
NK005(ca)013:4285: pa'i dbang du bgyis pa la nongs pa gang mchis
NK005(ca)013:4286: rtsa gsum srung ma dang bcas pa'i spyan sngar snying
NK005(ca)013:4287: nas bshags par bgyid pas bzod par mdzad du gsol
NK005(ca)013:4288: / blo las mi nus 'di khur ma mchis bzhin //
NK005(ca)013:4289: rgya chen bka' gzhung sdud pa'i ngal bas ci //
NK005(ca)013:4290: ru lu'i dgongs pa phyogs gcig rang rgyud la //
NK005(ca)013:4291: sbyor nas yib na bdag gzhan yid la 'jebs //
NK005(ca)013:4292: 'on kyang snga 'gyur rig 'dzin phyam gcig tu //
NK005(ca)013:4293: gshegs shul lam 'di smin gling gter chen rjes //
NK005(ca)013:4294: sa bon srog gi rtsa ba bzung mdzad kyang //
NK005(ca)013:4295: yan lag rgyas par spros par gal mdzad cing //
NK005(ca)013:4296: yig cha rnying pa'i don rnams 'byor dka' bas //
NK005(ca)013:4297: mos slob chos srid mkhan po rang 'dra ba'i //
NK005(ca)013:4298: gdung ba sel phyir lag len bdud rtsi'i bcud //
NK005(ca)013:4299: rgyud gzhung rin chen 'byung gnas che las phyung //
NK005(ca)013:4300: rig pa rnal 'byor gnyis kyis smin pa'i rgya //
NK005(ca)013:4301: tshom bu tshogs su sgrub pa'i nye rgyu yis //
NK005(ca)013:4302: brtol te sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK005(ca)013:4303: bde mchog yang dag sgrub pa mngon byed shog /
NK005(ca)013:4304: ces pa 'di ni dpal spungs yang khrod de b+ai
NK005(ca)013:4305: ko ti ts+aa 'dra rin chen brag tu rim gnyis
NK005(ca)013:4306: la gzhol ba'i 'dus pa rnams la nye bar mkho
NK005(ca)013:4308: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas pad+ma'i mtshan can sogs rdo rje
NK005(ca)013:4309: 'chang gnyis pa rnams kyis rjes su bzung ba'i rig
NK005(ca)013:4310: pa 'dzin pa'i gzugs brnyan pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug
NK005(ca)013:4311: blo gros mtha' yas pa'i sdes dpal chen lha khang
NK005(ca)013:4312: rdo rje bkod par sbyar ba dge legs 'phel //
NK005(ca)013:4313: dpal chen yang dag mtshan gyi zegs mas kyang //
NK005(ca)013:4314: sgrib gnyis kun sangs ye shes rgyas byed na //
NK005(ca)013:4315: tshom bu tshogs su bsgrubs pas rig 'dzin bzhi'i //
NK005(ca)013:4316: go 'phang bde blag 'grub pa lta ci smos //
NK005(ca)013:4317: tshul de'i lag len yig cha deng gi dus //
NK005(ca)013:4318: rnyed dka' u dum+wa ra'i mdzes rgyan 'di //
NK005(ca)013:4319: bsod nams gser gyi pad+ma 'dzum pa las //
NK005(ca)013:4320: legsa spyad zil dngar kun phan bcud grub pa //
NK005(ca)013:4321: chos blon gang des 'dzad med chos sbyin gyi //
NK005(ca)013:4322: gter du bsgrubs pa'i dge 'bras bsam yas des //
NK005(ca)013:4323: srid lam dub pa'i skye dgu ji snyed pa //
NK005(ca)013:4324: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde mchog bde thob shog /
